# game/episode018.rpy:28
translate spanish episode018_310347f3:

#   centered "{=chapter_heading}EPISODE 18{/=chapter_heading}"
    centered "{=chapter_heading}EPISODIO 18{/=chapter_heading}"

# game/episode018.rpy:46
translate spanish ep018_desert_f8966111:

#   "At first we were both elated by the thought that we were about to be rescued."
    "Al principio, los dos estábamos eufóricos pensando que nos iban a rescatar."

# game/episode018.rpy:47
translate spanish ep018_desert_8e67f8dd:

#   "As the engine noises intensified, our enthusiasm quickly waned."
    "A medida que se intensificaban los ruidos del motor, nuestro entusiasmo disminuía rápidamente."

# game/episode018.rpy:48
translate spanish ep018_desert_076fa781:

#   "It wasn’t the Bastard that was approaching our location, but the sounds of three different vehicles could now clearly be heard."
    "No era el Bastardo el que se acercaba a nuestra posición, pero ahora se oían claramente los sonidos de tres vehículos diferentes."

# game/episode018.rpy:50
translate spanish ep018_desert_0848870c:

#   c "Quick, behind those rocks!"
    c "¡Rápido, detrás de esas rocas!"

# game/episode018.rpy:51
translate spanish ep018_desert_db81cc94:

#   "We hastily gathered the sleeping bags and the backpack before fleeing behind the rocks."
    "Recogimos apresuradamente los sacos de dormir y la mochila antes de huir detrás de las rocas."

# game/episode018.rpy:53
translate spanish ep018_desert_46bb1cca:

#   "As we took position, three hover bikes came into view from behind a sand dune."
    "Cuando tomamos posición, tres motos aerodeslizadoras aparecieron detrás de una duna de arena."

# game/episode018.rpy:55
translate spanish ep018_desert_dfc2f82c:

#   "My heart sank when the bikes were close enough to make out its riders."
    "Se me encogió el corazón cuando las motos estuvieron lo bastante cerca como para distinguir a sus pilotos."

# game/episode018.rpy:56
translate spanish ep018_desert_fac01e77:

#   "Three of Glixken’s mercenaries were quickly closing in on the location we were hoping to spend the night just earlier."
    "Tres mercenarios de Glixken se acercaban rápidamente al lugar donde esperábamos pasar la noche."

# game/episode018.rpy:58
translate spanish ep018_desert_fab1b267:

#   "The mercenaries halted before the rocky outcropping."
    "Los mercenarios se detuvieron ante el afloramiento rocoso."

# game/episode018.rpy:59
translate spanish ep018_desert_ed92ae4c:

#   "They didn’t seem to have spotted us yet and were discussing something loud enough for us to hear."
    "No parecían habernos visto aún y estaban discutiendo algo en voz lo suficientemente alta como para que les oyéramos."

# game/episode018.rpy:64
translate spanish ep018_desert_a92d2b78:

#   man "This is supposed to be the site where they crashed, isn’t it?"
    man "Se supone que este es el sitio donde se estrellaron, ¿no?"

# game/episode018.rpy:65
translate spanish ep018_desert_0c5ad725:

#   man2 "Should be, yeah."
    man2 "Debería serlo, sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:66
translate spanish ep018_desert_5b0166fc:

#   man2 "But the location was approximate."
    man2 "Pero la ubicación era aproximada."

# game/episode018.rpy:67
translate spanish ep018_desert_b55648b3:

#   man "Approximate, my ass, there’s nothing here."
    man "Aproximado, una mierda, aquí no hay nada."

# game/episode018.rpy:68
translate spanish ep018_desert_968762cf:

#   "The mercs started bickering, so I whispered something in Eva’s ear."
    "Los mercenarios empezaron a discutir, así que susurré algo al oído de Eva."

# game/episode018.rpy:73
translate spanish ep018_desert_26f9102c:

#   c "We should take them now, while they don’t have their weapons within reach."
    c "Debemos tomarlos ahora, mientras no tengan sus armas al alcance."

# game/episode018.rpy:74
translate spanish ep018_desert_3086f694:

#   e "How?"
    e "¿Cómo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:75
translate spanish ep018_desert_79f39e64:

#   c "I think I can take one from here."
    c "Creo que puedo tomar uno de aquí."

# game/episode018.rpy:76
translate spanish ep018_desert_58806ec2:

#   c "Taking advantage of the confusion, I’m going to storm down and shoot the remaining two."
    c "Aprovechando la confusión, voy a irrumpir y disparar a los dos restantes."

# game/episode018.rpy:77
translate spanish ep018_desert_236cfd34:

#   c "There’s a pistol in the backpack, so you can give me cover fire."
    c "Hay una pistola en la mochila, así que puedes darme fuego de cobertura."

# game/episode018.rpy:79
translate spanish ep018_desert_7e3c47fa:

#   e "It’s been a while since I’ve held a gun, but I think I can manage that."
    e "Hace tiempo que no empuño un arma, pero creo que podré hacerlo."

# game/episode018.rpy:80
translate spanish ep018_desert_25eb3cbd:

#   c "Let’s get to it quickly, before they get their bearings or leave."
    c "Hagámoslo rápido, antes de que se orienten o se vayan."

# game/episode018.rpy:82
translate spanish ep018_desert_3a61a809:

#   "I unholstered my weapon and took aim at the nearest merc."
    "Desenfundé mi arma y apunté al mercenario más cercano."

# game/episode018.rpy:83
translate spanish ep018_desert_bab1c008:

#   "The mercs were still bickering over where to go next when I took my shot."
    "Los mercenarios seguían discutiendo sobre a dónde ir cuando disparé."

# game/episode018.rpy:85
translate spanish ep018_desert_333e6d08:

#   "Hitting a target from a distance like that was tricky, I knew that."
    "Dar en el blanco desde una distancia así era complicado, lo sabía."

# game/episode018.rpy:87
translate spanish ep018_desert_2de50e61:

#   "But I landed a lucky shot and as soon as I saw the guy’s chest explode, I started to sprint towards the two remaining mercs."
    "Pero acerté un tiro afortunado y, en cuanto vi explotar el pecho del tipo, empecé a correr hacia los dos mercenarios restantes."

# game/episode018.rpy:89
translate spanish ep018_desert_64038a71:

#   "Eva laid down cover fire, adding to the confusion."
    "Eva hizo fuego de cobertura, aumentando la confusión."

# game/episode018.rpy:90
translate spanish ep018_desert_731323ef:

#   "The mercs were frantically trying to retrieve their weapons from the bikes."
    "Los mercenarios intentaban frenéticamente recuperar sus armas de las motos."

# game/episode018.rpy:92
translate spanish ep018_desert_de5da721:

#   "I was upon them before they were able to turn around and shoot."
    "Estaba sobre ellos antes de que pudieran darse la vuelta y disparar."

# game/episode018.rpy:94
translate spanish ep018_desert_b5e08347:

#   "One of the mercs raised his weapon, but I shot him multiple times before he could even pull the trigger."
    "Uno de los mercenarios levantó el arma, pero le disparé varias veces antes de que pudiera apretar el gatillo."

# game/episode018.rpy:96
translate spanish ep018_desert_da2bdfaa:

#   "The remaining merc suddenly went to his knees."
    "El mercenario restante se arrodilló de repente."

# game/episode018.rpy:97
translate spanish ep018_desert_b48ff759:

#   "Eva had apparently scored a lucky shot."
    "Al parecer, Eva había tenido suerte."

# game/episode018.rpy:99
translate spanish ep018_desert_7dcd0b60:

#   "While I checked the three mercs for a pulse, Eva came towards me from the rocks."
    "Mientras comprobaba si los tres mercenarios tenían pulso, Eva se acercó a mí desde las rocas."

# game/episode018.rpy:101
translate spanish ep018_desert_7bc49e0f:

#   e "Did we get all of them?"
    e "¿Los tenemos todos?"

# game/episode018.rpy:102
translate spanish ep018_desert_57779ffa:

#   c "We did."
    c "Lo hicimos."

# game/episode018.rpy:103
translate spanish ep018_desert_47841cde:

#   c "It seems you did more than provide cover fire, you got at least one."
    c "Parece que hiciste más que proporcionar fuego de cobertura, conseguiste al menos uno."

# game/episode018.rpy:104
translate spanish ep018_desert_1a8ba5ca:

#   e "Guess that getting high grades in marksman training back at the Academy was good for something after all."
    e "Supongo que sacar buenas notas en el entrenamiento de tirador en la Academia sirvió para algo después de todo."

# game/episode018.rpy:105
translate spanish ep018_desert_82ebbb87:

#   c "It sure seems that way."
    c "Eso parece."

# game/episode018.rpy:107
translate spanish ep018_desert_b8416574:

#   e "Now what do we do?"
    e "¿Y ahora qué hacemos?"

# game/episode018.rpy:108
translate spanish ep018_desert_ec3e6790:

#   c "Search the bodies, we might find something useful."
    c "Registra los cuerpos, podríamos encontrar algo útil."

# game/episode018.rpy:109
translate spanish ep018_desert_82e3746c:

#   c "And of course we're taking their bikes."
    c "Y, por supuesto, nos llevamos sus bicicletas."

# game/episode018.rpy:111
translate spanish ep018_desert_efa3a5ba:

#   "The mercs were carrying an assortment of survival gear on their bikes, as well as all sorts of weaponry."
    "Los mercenarios llevaban un surtido de equipo de supervivencia en sus motos, así como todo tipo de armamento."

# game/episode018.rpy:112
translate spanish ep018_desert_385e6126:

#   e "These are flashbangs, aren't they?"
    e "Estos son flashbangs, ¿no?"

# game/episode018.rpy:113
translate spanish ep018_desert_ac4641e3:

#   c "Yup, smoke grenades too."
    c "Sí, granadas de humo también."

# game/episode018.rpy:115
translate spanish ep018_desert_c661fadb:

#   "Eva searched the bodies of the mercs, while I checked out the navigation computer of one of the bikes."
    "Eva registró los cuerpos de los mercenarios, mientras yo comprobaba el ordenador de navegación de una de las motos."

# game/episode018.rpy:116
translate spanish ep018_desert_8effe233:

#   "Each of the computers had registered the same route to a point several miles away."
    "Cada uno de los ordenadores había registrado la misma ruta hasta un punto situado a varios kilómetros de distancia."

# game/episode018.rpy:117
translate spanish ep018_desert_7fad21f4:

#   c "I think I found the location of the other mercs and possibly Glixken's ship."
    c "Creo que encontré la ubicación de los otros mercenarios y posiblemente la nave de Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:119
translate spanish ep018_desert_d2d05fd7:

#   e "So, do we steer clear of that area and search for our own ship?"
    e "Entonces, ¿nos alejamos de esa zona y buscamos nuestro propio barco?"

# game/episode018.rpy:120
translate spanish ep018_desert_5f053c4d:

#   c "I don't think these bikes are made for long-distance travel."
    c "No creo que estas motos estén hechas para viajes de larga distancia."

# game/episode018.rpy:121
translate spanish ep018_desert_e703784c:

#   c "Besides, these mercs didn't pack equipment capable of finding objects."
    c "Además, estos mercenarios no llevaban equipo capaz de encontrar objetos."

# game/episode018.rpy:122
translate spanish ep018_desert_7769823a:

#   c "I think we need to stage a surprise assault on their location."
    c "Creo que tenemos que organizar un asalto sorpresa en su ubicación."

# game/episode018.rpy:123
translate spanish ep018_desert_1025965a:

#   e "Just the two of us?"
    e "¿Sólo nosotros dos?"

# game/episode018.rpy:124
translate spanish ep018_desert_588cb7a0:

#   c "The radios the mercs were carrying list nine other contacts."
    c "Las radios que llevaban los mercenarios enumeran otros nueve contactos."

# game/episode018.rpy:125
translate spanish ep018_desert_76b32d60:

#   c "So if each of the other still living mercs carries a radio too, we'd be two up against seven."
    c "Así que si cada uno de los otros mercenarios aún vivos lleva una radio también, seríamos dos contra siete."

# game/episode018.rpy:126
translate spanish ep018_desert_432b2ef1:

#   c "We also have those bikes, grenades and the element of surprise."
    c "También tenemos las motos, las granadas y el elemento sorpresa."

# game/episode018.rpy:128
translate spanish ep018_desert_b3c3373d:

#   e "Risky..."
    e "Arriesgado..."

# game/episode018.rpy:129
translate spanish ep018_desert_8c49ba5f:

#   c "Very, but if we deal with Glixken and take his ship if it's still running, we might have a chance of finding our crew."
    c "Mucho, pero si tratamos con Glixken y tomamos su nave si aún funciona, podríamos tener una oportunidad de encontrar a nuestra tripulación."

# game/episode018.rpy:130
translate spanish ep018_desert_59468964:

#   c "According to the map in the nav computer, Glixken is holed up in a shallow crater, so we might be able to approach under some cover."
    c "Según el mapa del ordenador de navegación, Glixken está escondido en un cráter poco profundo, así que podríamos acercarnos a cubierto."

# game/episode018.rpy:131
translate spanish ep018_desert_dd082f8b:

#   c "Once we're close enough, we toss those flashbangs, maybe those smoke grenades and start shooting."
    c "Una vez que estemos lo suficientemente cerca, lanzamos las granadas de humo y empezamos a disparar."

# game/episode018.rpy:132
translate spanish ep018_desert_f3e7a0a9:

#   c "How are your shooting skills on a bike?"
    c "¿Qué tal se te da disparar en moto?"

# game/episode018.rpy:134
translate spanish ep018_desert_731680c4:

#   e "Passable."
    e "Pasable."

# game/episode018.rpy:135
translate spanish ep018_desert_cc1dbe7e:

#   c "That has to be good enough."
    c "Eso tiene que ser suficiente."

# game/episode018.rpy:136
translate spanish ep018_desert_3b9f7acb:

#   c "Let's go."
    c "Vámonos."

# game/episode018.rpy:138
translate spanish ep018_desert_e766e132:

#   "We sped away on our newly acquired bikes, leaving one of them behind with the corpses of the mercenaries."
    "Nos alejamos a toda velocidad en nuestras recién adquiridas motos, dejando atrás a uno de ellos con los cadáveres de los mercenarios."

# game/episode018.rpy:140
translate spanish ep018_desert_14652611:

#   "With every mile we came closer to the crater, the amount of adrenaline surged."
    "A cada kilómetro que nos acercábamos al cráter, aumentaba la adrenalina."

# game/episode018.rpy:142
translate spanish ep018_desert_0c38f74e:

#   "When the crater came into view, we slowed down to better observe our environment."
    "Cuando el cráter estuvo a la vista, redujimos la velocidad para observar mejor nuestro entorno."

# game/episode018.rpy:143
translate spanish ep018_desert_c5eff1d3:

#   "Glixken's ship seemed to have weathered its planetary insertion better than our craft did as no smoke column was visible from the crater."
    "La nave de Glixken parecía haber soportado mejor su inserción planetaria que la nuestra, ya que no se veía ninguna columna de humo desde el cráter."

# game/episode018.rpy:144
translate spanish ep018_desert_8b3614d5:

#   "No sentries were posted on the edge of the crater either, so Glixken must have felt himself safe from any threat."
    "Tampoco había centinelas apostados en el borde del cráter, así que Glixken debió de sentirse a salvo de cualquier amenaza."

# game/episode018.rpy:145
translate spanish ep018_desert_ac6cce05:

#   "We left our bikes outside hearing distance and walked towards the edge to survey the situation inside the crater."
    "Dejamos las bicicletas fuera del alcance de la vista y caminamos hacia el borde para observar la situación dentro del cráter."

# game/episode018.rpy:147
translate spanish ep018_desert_6b2ece1a:

#   "My assumptions about the state of the mercenary ship were confirmed, as most of the spacecraft seemed to be intact."
    "Mis suposiciones sobre el estado de la nave mercenaria se confirmaron, ya que la mayor parte de la nave parecía estar intacta."

# game/episode018.rpy:148
translate spanish ep018_desert_93abe6dd:

#   "There were only four mercs visible, two doing repairs, while another two patrolled the area."
    "Sólo había cuatro mercenarios visibles, dos haciendo reparaciones y otros dos patrullando la zona."

# game/episode018.rpy:150
translate spanish ep018_desert_116a8865:

#   e "Only four of them?"
    e "¿Sólo cuatro?"

# game/episode018.rpy:151
translate spanish ep018_desert_6b399da6:

#   e "That makes our job easier, doesn't it?"
    e "Eso nos facilita el trabajo, ¿no?"

# game/episode018.rpy:152
translate spanish ep018_desert_61daf6c7:

#   c "Glixken and the other two could be inside."
    c "Glixken y los otros dos podrían estar dentro."

# game/episode018.rpy:153
translate spanish ep018_desert_2b870526:

#   c "All doors are closed, so getting inside and eliminating the remaining three of them could prove difficult."
    c "Todas las puertas están cerradas, por lo que entrar y eliminar a los tres restantes podría resultar difícil."

# game/episode018.rpy:155
translate spanish ep018_desert_95353413:

#   e "Do you want to wait to see if they're there?"
    e "¿Quieres esperar a ver si están ahí?"

# game/episode018.rpy:156
translate spanish ep018_desert_77514f8a:

#   c "Might be best."
    c "Podría ser lo mejor."

# game/episode018.rpy:158
translate spanish ep018_desert_a45f466e:

#   "We tried and failed to distinguish any life inside the ship for several minutes."
    "Durante varios minutos intentamos distinguir vida en el interior del barco, pero no lo conseguimos."

# game/episode018.rpy:159
translate spanish ep018_desert_334a6931:

#   c "I don't think they're here."
    c "No creo que estén aquí."

# game/episode018.rpy:160
translate spanish ep018_desert_7e7797ed:

#   c "Let's head back to the bikes and stage our assault."
    c "Volvamos a las motos y preparemos nuestro asalto."

# game/episode018.rpy:161
translate spanish ep018_desert_abec3592:

#   c "Dealing with Glixken will be much easier once we control his ship."
    c "Tratar con Glixken será mucho más fácil una vez que controlemos su nave."

# game/episode018.rpy:163
translate spanish ep018_desert_c7b99256:

#   "We were about to turn around when Eva pointed into the distance across the crater."
    "Estábamos a punto de dar la vuelta cuando Eva señaló a lo lejos, al otro lado del cráter."

# game/episode018.rpy:164
translate spanish ep018_desert_4ca55afe:

#   e "Someone's coming!"
    e "¡Alguien viene!"

# game/episode018.rpy:168
translate spanish ep018_desert_706bbd13:

#   "Dust clouds were billowing on the horizon."
    "En el horizonte se veían nubes de polvo."

# game/episode018.rpy:170
translate spanish ep018_desert_f412e7f1:

#   "Three bikes emerged from the dust and swooped down into the crater."
    "Tres motos emergieron del polvo y descendieron en picado hacia el cráter."

# game/episode018.rpy:171
translate spanish ep018_desert_46a9734b:

#   "Glixken and two of his men had returned."
    "Glixken y dos de sus hombres habían regresado."

# game/episode018.rpy:172
translate spanish ep018_desert_5ad23b1e:

#   "What was draped across the back of each bike turned our moods very sour."
    "Lo que cubría la parte trasera de cada moto nos puso de muy mal humor."

# game/episode018.rpy:174
translate spanish ep018_desert_e8e190ec:

#   e "Fuck, they've captured Thyia, Aven and Lilly!"
    e "¡Joder, han capturado a Thyia, Aven y Lilly!"

# game/episode018.rpy:175
translate spanish ep018_desert_1cb99783:

#   c "They seem to be trussed up, so I think they're still alive."
    c "Parecen estar atados, así que creo que todavía están vivos."

# game/episode018.rpy:176
translate spanish ep018_desert_ce334cf1:

#   e "I hope the rest of the crew didn't suffer a worse fate."
    e "Espero que el resto de la tripulación no sufriera un destino peor."

# game/episode018.rpy:177
translate spanish ep018_desert_ccb180c0:

#   c "No time to worry about that, we have to strike now."
    c "No hay tiempo para preocuparse por eso, tenemos que atacar ahora."

# game/episode018.rpy:179
translate spanish ep018_desert_99e82a99:

#   gl "Look what we brought in!"
    gl "¡Mira lo que hemos traído!"

# game/episode018.rpy:180
translate spanish ep018_desert_cb8d6816:

#   gl "Three stray cunts, wandering the desert."
    gl "Tres vagabundos, vagando por el desierto."

# game/episode018.rpy:181
translate spanish ep018_desert_2e16d171:

#   gl "And one of them is so very familiar."
    gl "Y uno de ellos me resulta muy familiar."

# game/episode018.rpy:182
translate spanish ep018_desert_36794910:

#   gl "Such a small universe..."
    gl "Un universo tan pequeño..."

# game/episode018.rpy:184
translate spanish ep018_desert_f8556e14:

#   gl "Say hi to the boys, Thyia."
    gl "Saluda a los chicos, Thyia."

# game/episode018.rpy:186
translate spanish ep018_desert_359e5d2d:

#   th "Fuck you!"
    th "¡Que te jodan!"

# game/episode018.rpy:187
translate spanish ep018_desert_6f19aa5d:

#   gl "Now, now, I'm sure you'll talk differently when we're done with you."
    gl "Seguro que hablarás de otra manera cuando acabemos contigo."

# game/episode018.rpy:188
translate spanish ep018_desert_4b8522ee:

#   gl "We'll teach you to say 'Thank you, sir' and 'Give me more, sir' when you have the privilege of sucking our cocks."
    gl "Te enseñaremos a decir \"Gracias, señor\" y \"Deme más, señor\" cuando tengas el privilegio de chuparnos la polla."

# game/episode018.rpy:190
translate spanish ep018_desert_03ec59f8:

#   l "Thyia, are you alright?!"
    l "Thyia, ¿estás bien?"

# game/episode018.rpy:192
translate spanish ep018_desert_a37529cf:

#   gl "Your friend is fine, I was just telling about how we're about to gang rape the three of you."
    gl "Tu amigo está bien, sólo estaba contando que estamos a punto de violaros en grupo a los tres."

# game/episode018.rpy:194
translate spanish ep018_desert_05cdce70:

#   l "Is that supposed to scare me, you miserable fucking space lizard?!"
    l "¡¿Se supone que eso debe asustarme, maldita lagartija espacial miserable?!"

# game/episode018.rpy:196
translate spanish ep018_desert_70a975b4:

#   gl "Again with the insults."
    gl "Otra vez con los insultos."

# game/episode018.rpy:197
translate spanish ep018_desert_5afcce17:

#   gl "Tear their pathetic armor off so we can show them a lesson, boys."
    gl "Arrancadles su patética armadura para que podamos darles una lección, chicos."

# game/episode018.rpy:199
translate spanish ep018_desert_3c132b67:

#   gl "Walgx, is the ship repaired?"
    gl "Walgx, ¿está reparada la nave?"

# game/episode018.rpy:202
translate spanish ep018_desert_989ee5b6:

#   man "Almost, boss."
    man "Casi, jefe."

# game/episode018.rpy:204
translate spanish ep018_desert_472f498c:

#   gl "Work harder then, or you'll be the last to have your way with any of these bitches."
    gl "Trabaja más duro entonces, o serás el último en salirte con la tuya con alguna de estas zorras."

# game/episode018.rpy:206
translate spanish ep018_desert_20706d0e:

#   man2 "What the-"
    man2 "¿Qué...?"

# game/episode018.rpy:207
translate spanish ep018_desert_afb7e4d4:

#   gl "We're under attack!!!"
    gl "¡¡¡Nos atacan!!!"

# game/episode018.rpy:210
translate spanish ep018_desert_cf3f60cd:

#   "The first flashbang blinded everyone, except the mechanic working on Glixken's ship."
    "La primera explosión cegó a todos, excepto al mecánico que trabajaba en la nave de Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:211
translate spanish ep018_desert_8d95f90e:

#   "Both our bikes barreled down into the crater as we took aim at the mercs who were desperately trying to shake off their temporary blindness."
    "Nuestras dos motos se precipitaron hacia el cráter mientras apuntábamos a los mercenarios que intentaban desesperadamente librarse de su ceguera temporal."

# game/episode018.rpy:212
translate spanish ep018_desert_b59830fb:

#   "Eva aimed for the mercs who weren't standing close to Lilly, Thyia and Aven."
    "Eva apuntó a los mercenarios que no estaban cerca de Lilly, Thyia y Aven."

# game/episode018.rpy:213
translate spanish ep018_desert_9566ca16:

#   "I tried to find the mechanic, but he had gone to cover."
    "Intenté encontrar al mecánico, pero se había ido a cubrir."

# game/episode018.rpy:215
translate spanish ep018_desert_254d7785:

#   "Two mercs were already dead by the time the initial chaos lifted."
    "Dos mercenarios ya estaban muertos cuando se levantó el caos inicial."

# game/episode018.rpy:217
translate spanish ep018_desert_60be9f31:

#   "Aven and Lilly had somehow managed to knock over a third and were trying to subdue him while still affected by blindness."
    "Aven y Lilly se las habían arreglado de algún modo para derribar a un tercero e intentaban someterlo mientras seguía afectado por la ceguera."

# game/episode018.rpy:219
translate spanish ep018_desert_d3a8dbd5:

#   "The two other mercs had a weapon in their hands and were about to shoot at us."
    "Los otros dos mercenarios tenían un arma en la mano y estaban a punto de dispararnos."

# game/episode018.rpy:220
translate spanish ep018_desert_c8106953:

#   "Glixken, nor Thyia were anywhere in sight."
    "Glixken, ni Thyia estaban a la vista."

# game/episode018.rpy:221
translate spanish ep018_desert_647e3e33:

#   "Eva's bike was hit by a desperate volley from one of the mercs."
    "La moto de Eva fue alcanzada por una descarga desesperada de uno de los mercenarios."

# game/episode018.rpy:223
translate spanish ep018_desert_fb69e8e2:

#   "Her bike went down, but she managed to jump off of it before it crashed into the sand."
    "Su moto se vino abajo, pero consiguió saltar de ella antes de que se estrellara contra la arena."

# game/episode018.rpy:225
translate spanish ep018_desert_5adfe18a:

#   "I managed to evade the shots and ran over the other mercenary, his head sheared off by the bike, before he could pull the trigger."
    "Conseguí esquivar los disparos y atropellé al otro mercenario, con la cabeza destrozada por la moto, antes de que pudiera apretar el gatillo."

# game/episode018.rpy:227
translate spanish ep018_desert_757bf32c:

#   "Eva took care of the remaining merc from behind the cover of her bike."
    "Eva se ocupó de los mercenarios restantes desde detrás de la cubierta de su moto."

# game/episode018.rpy:228
translate spanish ep018_desert_565112cc:

#   "That left Glixken and the mechanic."
    "Quedaban Glixken y el mecánico."

# game/episode018.rpy:230
translate spanish ep018_desert_4c1d8dfb:

#   c "Eva, cover me!"
    c "¡Eva, cúbreme!"

# game/episode018.rpy:231
translate spanish ep018_desert_725a235e:

#   "Glixken was probably trying to make an escape with his ship, so I sprinted towards the entrance hatch."
    "Glixken probablemente intentaba escapar con su nave, así que corrí hacia la escotilla de entrada."

# game/episode018.rpy:233
translate spanish ep018_desert_504917cc:

#   "I found the engineer working frantically near the entrance, probably trying to hotwire the hatch to close."
    "Encontré al ingeniero trabajando frenéticamente cerca de la entrada, probablemente intentando forzar la escotilla para que se cerrara."

# game/episode018.rpy:235
translate spanish ep018_desert_eb20642c:

#   "The merc turned his surprised face towards me as two well-placed shots were already about to hit him."
    "El mercenario volvió su cara de sorpresa hacia mí cuando dos disparos bien colocados ya estaban a punto de alcanzarle."

# game/episode018.rpy:236
translate spanish ep018_desert_da67163a:

#   "He went down instantly."
    "Cayó al instante."

# game/episode018.rpy:238
translate spanish ep018_desert_b98e6e2c:

#   "With Eva following me close, I entered the ship."
    "Con Eva siguiéndome de cerca, entré en la nave."

# game/episode018.rpy:240
translate spanish ep018_desert_29485790:

#   "Glixken and Thyia weren't in the cockpit, so we did a room-by-room search."
    "Glixken y Thyia no estaban en la cabina, así que hicimos una búsqueda habitación por habitación."

# game/episode018.rpy:241
translate spanish ep018_desert_3e633d46:

#   c "Clear."
    c "Despejado."

# game/episode018.rpy:243
translate spanish ep018_desert_9943d0b8:

#   "We made our way further into the ship."
    "Nos adentramos en el barco."

# game/episode018.rpy:244
translate spanish ep018_desert_361b690f:

#   "I had a feeling we would find at least Glixken in the engine room, probably trying to get the ship running in a hurry."
    "Tenía la sensación de que encontraríamos al menos a Glixken en la sala de máquinas, probablemente intentando poner la nave en marcha a toda prisa."

# game/episode018.rpy:246
translate spanish ep018_desert_145d9349:

#   "My thought was confirmed when I heard Glixken barking an order."
    "Mi pensamiento se confirmó cuando oí a Glixken ladrar una orden."

# game/episode018.rpy:247
translate spanish ep018_desert_d169ae0e:

#   gl "Work faster, bitch!"
    gl "¡Trabaja más rápido, perra!"

# game/episode018.rpy:248
translate spanish ep018_desert_931ff30f:

#   "I wordlessly motioned Eva to follow me."
    "Le hice un gesto a Eva para que me siguiera."

# game/episode018.rpy:250
translate spanish ep018_desert_c7ed77a7:

#   "Glixken was standing amongst a jungle of hanging wires, some of them sparking with electricity."
    "Glixken estaba de pie entre una jungla de cables colgantes, algunos de los cuales echaban chispas de electricidad."

# game/episode018.rpy:251
translate spanish ep018_desert_1fb5c93e:

#   "He was pointing a gun at Thyia, who was crouched over some machinery, tools scattered around her."
    "Apuntaba con una pistola a Thyia, que estaba agachada sobre una maquinaria, con las herramientas esparcidas a su alrededor."

# game/episode018.rpy:252
translate spanish ep018_desert_aa2778e9:

#   c "Drop your weapons!"
    c "¡Tiren sus armas!"

# game/episode018.rpy:254
translate spanish ep018_desert_991a7011:

#   "Glixken whirled on us, still pointing one gun on Thyia."
    "Glixken giró sobre nosotros, todavía apuntando con un arma a Thyia."

# game/episode018.rpy:256
translate spanish ep018_desert_8d48e7cb:

#   "Thyia caught my eye and looked deliberately at the hanging wires behind Glixken's back."
    "Thyia me llamó la atención y miró deliberadamente los cables que colgaban a espaldas de Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:260
translate spanish ep018_desert_caf8449b:

#   "Letting Thyia do anything to endanger herself seemed too much of a gamble, especially considering we had two guns trained on Glixken."
    "Dejar que Thyia hiciera algo que la pusiera en peligro parecía demasiado arriesgado, sobre todo teniendo en cuenta que teníamos dos armas apuntando a Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:262
translate spanish ep018_desert_1bfe4b74:

#   "Without warning, I shot Glixken."
    "Sin previo aviso, disparé a Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:263
translate spanish ep018_desert_285bc661:

#   "The mercenary boss took two shots in the chest and the final one going through his head."
    "El jefe mercenario recibió dos disparos en el pecho y el último le atravesó la cabeza."

# game/episode018.rpy:265
translate spanish ep018_desert_390486e6:

#   "In his final moments, he managed to pull the trigger himself."
    "En sus últimos momentos, consiguió apretar él mismo el gatillo."

# game/episode018.rpy:266
translate spanish ep018_desert_454ef8b0:

#   "The aim of his rifle pointed at us went completely off."
    "La puntería de su rifle apuntándonos se desvió por completo."

# game/episode018.rpy:267
translate spanish ep018_desert_a1184f35:

#   "The shots from his other gun grazed Thyia, who went down with a yelp."
    "Los disparos de su otra arma rozaron a Thyia, que cayó con un aullido."

# game/episode018.rpy:271
translate spanish ep018_desert_d8c190e0:

#   "I decided to follow Thyia's lead and stalled Glixken."
    "Decidí seguir el ejemplo de Thyia y paralicé a Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:272
translate spanish ep018_desert_6c389f65:

#   c "I won't ask again, drop your weapons."
    c "No volveré a preguntar, tiren sus armas."

# game/episode018.rpy:273
translate spanish ep018_desert_b9916eeb:

#   gl "Are you going to shoot me, boy?"
    gl "¿Vas a dispararme, muchacho?"

# game/episode018.rpy:274
translate spanish ep018_desert_e03b9a70:

#   gl "You know I'm quicker."
    gl "Sabes que soy más rápido."

# game/episode018.rpy:275
translate spanish ep018_desert_94540f44:

#   gl "I'll take you out first, maybe only cripple the blonde."
    gl "Te eliminaré primero, tal vez sólo lisiaré a la rubia."

# game/episode018.rpy:277
translate spanish ep018_desert_ecec6172:

#   gl "After all, women aren't that fun to fuck when they're dead."
    gl "Después de todo, las mujeres no son tan divertidas de follar cuando están muertas."

# game/episode018.rpy:278
translate spanish ep018_desert_97182106:

#   c "Man...{w} All you ever do is make these tired rape threats."
    c "Hombre ... {w} Todo lo que siempre haces es hacer estas amenazas de violación cansado."

# game/episode018.rpy:279
translate spanish ep018_desert_d59bd92d:

#   c "I'd wager a limp-dick lizard like you would come up with something more original."
    c "Apostaría a que a un lagarto de pito flojo como tú se le ocurriría algo más original."

# game/episode018.rpy:280
translate spanish ep018_desert_fff33fc1:

#   "Glixken's reply to that particular comment would forever be a mystery to anyone currently in the engine room."
    "La respuesta de Glixken a ese comentario en particular sería para siempre un misterio para cualquiera que se encontrara actualmente en la sala de máquinas."

# game/episode018.rpy:282
translate spanish ep018_desert_00264734:

#   "Thyia had come up from her crouch and grabbed one of the sparkling wires."
    "Thyia se había levantado de su cuclillas y había agarrado uno de los cables brillantes."

# game/episode018.rpy:284
translate spanish ep018_desert_00a02237:

#   "When Glixken's opened his mouth to reply, she pressed the end of the sparking cable against the mercenary's neck."
    "Cuando Glixken abrió la boca para responder, ella apretó el extremo del cable chispeante contra el cuello del mercenario."

# game/episode018.rpy:285
translate spanish ep018_desert_7319fcf8:

#   "Glixken started screaming and shuddering, smoke rising from behind the top of his head."
    "Glixken empezó a gritar y a estremecerse, con humo saliendo de su cabeza."

# game/episode018.rpy:287
translate spanish ep018_desert_c33a5644:

#   "He fell on his knees with a heavy thud, the smell of burned lizard flesh filling the engine room."
    "Cayó de rodillas con un fuerte golpe y el olor a carne de lagarto quemada llenó la sala de máquinas."

# game/episode018.rpy:289
translate spanish ep018_desert_93b0863f:

#   "The mercenary's eyes glazed over and he collapsed face-first onto the floor."
    "Al mercenario se le pusieron los ojos vidriosos y cayó de bruces al suelo."

# game/episode018.rpy:291
translate spanish ep018_desert_00e752c0:

#   "I moved in quickly and shot him through the head to make sure he wasn't getting up again soon."
    "Me acerqué rápidamente y le disparé en la cabeza para asegurarme de que no volvía a levantarse pronto."

# game/episode018.rpy:296
translate spanish ep018_desert_1a1ef9d1:

#   c "Are you alright, Thyia?"
    c "¿Estás bien, Thyia?"

# game/episode018.rpy:299
translate spanish ep018_desert_6d07948e:

#   th "It's just a light flesh wound, I think."
    th "Es sólo una herida superficial leve, creo."

# game/episode018.rpy:300
translate spanish ep018_desert_295ad919:

#   "Thyia was bleeding from her shoulder, but it didn't look that serious."
    "Thyia sangraba por el hombro, pero no parecía tan grave."

# game/episode018.rpy:302
translate spanish ep018_desert_48b528e8:

#   th "I did have a plan, you know, which you ruined by shooting him first!"
    th "¡Tenía un plan, que arruinaste disparándole primero!"

# game/episode018.rpy:303
translate spanish ep018_desert_338c233e:

#   c "Your gamble could have backfired, and I had a clear shot."
    c "Su apuesta podría haber sido contraproducente, y yo tenía una oportunidad clara."

# game/episode018.rpy:305
translate spanish ep018_desert_61178b61:

#   th "Fair enough, my shoulder just fucking hurts."
    th "Está bien, me duele el hombro."

# game/episode018.rpy:307
translate spanish ep018_desert_74869e95:

#   c "We have painkillers in the mercs’ supply and after that Thim can take a look."
    c "Tenemos analgésicos en el suministro de mercenarios y después de que Thim puede echar un vistazo."

# game/episode018.rpy:309
translate spanish ep018_desert_f4eb7e2f:

#   c "We have painkillers in the mercs’ supply and after that the autodoc can take a look."
    c "Tenemos analgésicos en el suministro de mercenarios y después de que el autodoc puede echar un vistazo."

# game/episode018.rpy:311
translate spanish ep018_desert_d22896bb:

#   th "A little bruised here and there."
    th "Un poco magullado aquí y allá."

# game/episode018.rpy:312
translate spanish ep018_desert_58e4c475:

#   "Thyia only looked a little frazzled."
    "Thyia sólo parecía un poco agotada."

# game/episode018.rpy:314
translate spanish ep018_desert_ef7fb04d:

#   c "I guess that's the end of Glixken and his band of merry men..."
    c "Supongo que es el fin de Glixken y su banda de hombres alegres..."

# game/episode018.rpy:315
translate spanish ep018_desert_759d5c91:

#   th "Couldn't have happened to a nicer guy."
    th "No podría haberle pasado a un tipo más agradable."

# game/episode018.rpy:316
translate spanish ep018_desert_47584612:

#   e "How did you end up in their hands?"
    e "¿Cómo acabaste en sus manos?"

# game/episode018.rpy:318
translate spanish ep018_desert_1736bfc0:

#   th "After we crashed onto this planet, we quickly made some emergency repairs."
    th "Después de estrellarnos en este planeta, hicimos rápidamente algunas reparaciones de emergencia."

# game/episode018.rpy:319
translate spanish ep018_desert_d3bcb46d:

#   th "Jade and Céline worked on expanding the range of the ship's scanners."
    th "Jade y Céline trabajaron para ampliar el alcance de los escáneres de la nave."

# game/episode018.rpy:320
translate spanish ep018_desert_ae40f95e:

#   th "After picking up several anomalies, the three of us went out to scout the area."
    th "Tras detectar varias anomalías, los tres salimos a explorar la zona."

# game/episode018.rpy:321
translate spanish ep018_desert_8d9a9008:

#   th "Glixken intercepted our party soon after and took us back here."
    th "Glixken interceptó a nuestro grupo poco después y nos trajo de vuelta aquí."

# game/episode018.rpy:323
translate spanish ep018_desert_1d57beb7:

#   th "But I'm so glad to see you both in one piece."
    th "Pero me alegro mucho de veros a los dos de una pieza."

# game/episode018.rpy:324
translate spanish ep018_desert_4962a45f:

#   th "Did your ship survive the landing?"
    th "¿Sobrevivió tu barco al desembarco?"

# game/episode018.rpy:325
translate spanish ep018_desert_7f79c2e3:

#   c "It didn't."
    c "No fue así."

# game/episode018.rpy:326
translate spanish ep018_desert_f2cba749:

#   c "We were lucky to ambush three of Glixken's men."
    c "Tuvimos suerte de emboscar a tres hombres de Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:328
translate spanish ep018_desert_42750aef:

#   e "The bikes they rode contained information about their location, so we staged an assault."
    e "Las motos que conducían contenían información sobre su ubicación, así que organizamos un asalto."

# game/episode018.rpy:330
translate spanish ep018_desert_e6e2ba75:

#   th "Just the two of you?"
    th "¿Sólo vosotros dos?"

# game/episode018.rpy:331
translate spanish ep018_desert_491efc0b:

#   c "We kind of needed a space ship..."
    c "Necesitábamos una nave espacial..."

# game/episode018.rpy:333
translate spanish ep018_desert_efb66d52:

#   e "And now we have two."
    e "Y ahora tenemos dos."

# game/episode018.rpy:334
translate spanish ep018_desert_eb03520b:

#   c "We sure do."
    c "Claro que sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:335
translate spanish ep018_desert_4f3d73f0:

#   c "But I'm not about to start a fleet of ships."
    c "Pero no voy a empezar una flota de barcos."

# game/episode018.rpy:336
translate spanish ep018_desert_c81ed443:

#   c "Let's use Glixken's bucket as a taxi and go find the others outside."
    c "Usemos el cubo de Glixken como taxi y vayamos a buscar a los demás fuera."

# game/episode018.rpy:337
translate spanish ep018_desert_13fa9b1d:

#   c "Do you think we can radio the Bastard from here?"
    c "¿Crees que podemos llamar al Bastardo por radio desde aquí?"

# game/episode018.rpy:339
translate spanish ep018_desert_9051c269:

#   th "If the comms on this ship work, I think it should be possible."
    th "Si las comunicaciones de esta nave funcionan, creo que debería ser posible."

# game/episode018.rpy:341
translate spanish ep018_desert_355fd1d0:

#   "Lilly and Aven were just as happy to see us."
    "Lilly y Aven estaban igual de contentos de vernos."

# game/episode018.rpy:343
translate spanish ep018_desert_8b68f19a:

#   "After we brought them up to speed, we went to the bridge of the ship and contacted the Bastard."
    "Después de ponerlos al corriente, fuimos al puente de la nave y contactamos con el Bastardo."

# game/episode018.rpy:344
translate spanish ep018_desert_f53eab64:

#   "Céline was ecstatic to hear from us and we agreed to fly Glixken's ship to their location."
    "Céline se quedó extasiada al saber de nosotros y accedimos a llevar el barco de Glixken hasta su ubicación."

# game/episode018.rpy:346
translate spanish ep018_desert_ce273275:

#   "We brought the bikes that were undamaged in the fight back into the ship."
    "Llevamos al barco las motos que no sufrieron daños en la pelea."

# game/episode018.rpy:347
translate spanish ep018_desert_fab1dbd8:

#   "The corpses of Glixken and the engineer were dragged and dumped outside."
    "Los cadáveres de Glixken y el ingeniero fueron arrastrados y arrojados fuera."

# game/episode018.rpy:352
translate spanish ep018_desert_9a51c5c7:

#   "Burying the mercs seemed too much of an honor, so we left them to decompose in the planet's harsh climate."
    "Enterrar a los mercenarios parecía demasiado honor, así que los dejamos descomponerse en el duro clima del planeta."

# game/episode018.rpy:353
translate spanish ep018_desert_33cb4937:

#   "We took off in the direction of our crew a relatively short distance away."
    "Despegamos en dirección a nuestra tripulación, a una distancia relativamente corta."

# game/episode018.rpy:355
translate spanish ep018_desert_4946a644:

#   "From the air, the Bastard didn't seem to have sustained that much damage."
    "Desde el aire, el Bastardo no parecía haber sufrido tanto daño."

# game/episode018.rpy:357
translate spanish ep018_desert_a1733a8d:

#   "We were welcomed by each of the crew, who mercifully survived the pursuit by Glixken and subsequent emergency landing."
    "Fuimos recibidos por cada uno de los tripulantes, que afortunadamente sobrevivieron a la persecución de Glixken y al posterior aterrizaje de emergencia."

# game/episode018.rpy:359
translate spanish ep018_desert_c76f1b3e:

#   "Thyia, Céline and Jade remained on the bridge to discuss the state of repair of the Bastard."
    "Thyia, Céline y Jade permanecieron en el puente para discutir el estado de reparación del Bastardo."

# game/episode018.rpy:360
translate spanish ep018_desert_70ab317e:

#   j "All systems are running optimally now."
    j "Todos los sistemas funcionan ahora de forma óptima."

# game/episode018.rpy:362
translate spanish ep018_desert_4493da5a:

#   j "Those repairs to the electrical grid seem to be holding."
    j "Las reparaciones de la red eléctrica parecen estar aguantando."

# game/episode018.rpy:364
translate spanish ep018_desert_da6c83fd:

#   ce "Yes, I think we can take her to space again."
    ce "Sí, creo que podemos llevarla al espacio otra vez."

# game/episode018.rpy:366
translate spanish ep018_desert_5fd8afd5:

#   th "The Bastard spending some time in a dry dock might not be a bad idea in the near future."
    th "Que el Bastardo pase algún tiempo en dique seco podría no ser una mala idea en un futuro próximo."

# game/episode018.rpy:367
translate spanish ep018_desert_320cdb62:

#   c "Agreed, but the mission comes first."
    c "De acuerdo, pero la misión es lo primero."

# game/episode018.rpy:368
translate spanish ep018_desert_906350cb:

#   th "Naturally."
    th "Naturalmente."

# game/episode018.rpy:369
translate spanish ep018_desert_30cb866c:

#   th "What are you planning to do with the mercenary ship?"
    th "¿Qué piensas hacer con el barco mercenario?"

# game/episode018.rpy:370
translate spanish ep018_desert_a269ecd4:

#   c "I don't know, can we salvage it for parts?"
    c "No sé, ¿podemos recuperarlo para piezas?"

# game/episode018.rpy:371
translate spanish ep018_desert_4ce91e2f:

#   th "Sure."
    th "Sí, claro."

# game/episode018.rpy:372
translate spanish ep018_desert_ede90c0c:

#   th "Jade, can you run a diagnostic and see what we can rip from it."
    th "Jade, ¿puedes hacer un diagnóstico y ver qué podemos extraer de él?"

# game/episode018.rpy:374
translate spanish ep018_desert_7742c481:

#   j "On it, I'll start right away."
    j "En ello, voy a empezar de inmediato."

# game/episode018.rpy:376
translate spanish ep018_desert_41e59a3f:

#   c "You should get that shoulder looked at, Thyia."
    c "Deberías hacerte mirar ese hombro, Thyia."

# game/episode018.rpy:378
translate spanish ep018_desert_fdb0498b:

#   c "You should get those bruises looked at, Thyia, just to be sure."
    c "Deberías hacerte mirar esos moratones, Thyia, para estar segura."

# game/episode018.rpy:381
translate spanish ep018_desert_8285e0b1:

#   th "Fine, I'll pay a visit to Dr. Von Skanderfelt."
    th "Bien, le haré una visita al Dr. Von Skanderfelt."

# game/episode018.rpy:384
translate spanish ep018_desert_0c6309f3:

#   th "Fine, I'll pay a visit to the autodoc."
    th "Bien, haré una visita al autodoc."

# game/episode018.rpy:385
translate spanish ep018_desert_cd95b252:

#   th "For the record, that robot has a terrible bedside manner."
    th "Que conste que ese robot tiene unos modales terribles."

# game/episode018.rpy:387
translate spanish ep018_desert_84ed0a9a:

#   "Céline resumed her work on the bridge leaving me to check up on the crew."
    "Céline reanudó su trabajo en el puente y yo me ocupé de la tripulación."

# game/episode018.rpy:391
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_22dfdb47:

#   "A couple of hours later, I got an excited message from Jade, asking me to visit her on Glixken's ship."
    "Un par de horas después, recibí un emocionado mensaje de Jade, pidiéndome que la visitara en la nave de Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:394
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_b472bb2f:

#   c "What's gotten you excited all of a sudden?"
    c "¿Qué le ha entusiasmado de repente?"

# game/episode018.rpy:396
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_81ebc4f7:

#   j "While going through the ship's computer, I've managed to unearth some logs kept by Glixken, master."
    j "Mientras revisaba el ordenador de la nave, he conseguido desenterrar algunos registros guardados por Glixken, maestro."

# game/episode018.rpy:397
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_1d9fdff7:

#   c "So, what did you learn?"
    c "¿Qué has aprendido?"

# game/episode018.rpy:399
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_a4444079:

#   c "Don't tell me you've found conclusive evidence of Glixken secretly being a tender-hearted hero of the people?"
    c "¿No me digas que has encontrado pruebas concluyentes de que Glixken es en secreto un tierno héroe del pueblo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:401
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_98843553:

#   j "Nope, he's still the recently departed raping mercenary everyone so fondly remembers..."
    j "No, sigue siendo el mercenario violador recientemente fallecido que todos recuerdan con tanto cariño..."

# game/episode018.rpy:402
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_a46bceba:

#   j "In fact, some of his crimes are detailed in the log he kept in the ship's computer."
    j "De hecho, algunos de sus crímenes se detallan en el diario que guardaba en el ordenador de la nave."

# game/episode018.rpy:403
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_68df38ff:

#   j "I've just managed to crack it."
    j "Acabo de conseguir descifrarlo."

# game/episode018.rpy:405
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_0c28d7c4:

#   j "It seems that woman, the Bloodhound, has recruited him on Vulpes Velox, even before we visited the Theater of Senses."
    j "Parece que esa mujer, la Bloodhound, lo ha reclutado en Vulpes Velox, incluso antes de que visitáramos el Teatro de los Sentidos."

# game/episode018.rpy:406
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_0e7a6a30:

#   c "Kvi hired him?"
    c "¿Kvi lo contrató?"

# game/episode018.rpy:407
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_29c2709e:

#   j "She promised him Thyia, among other things, apparently."
    j "Ella le prometió Thyia, entre otras cosas, al parecer."

# game/episode018.rpy:408
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_7885cdaf:

#   j "They weren't very successful on Kepler, but Kvi retained them despite their failure."
    j "No tuvieron mucho éxito en Kepler, pero Kvi los conservó a pesar de su fracaso."

# game/episode018.rpy:409
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_14367873:

#   j "They were sent out once more to find us during the assault on Taagmar, though there were objections."
    j "Fueron enviados una vez más a buscarnos durante el asalto a Taagmar, aunque hubo objeciones."

# game/episode018.rpy:410
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_e15cec45:

#   c "Objections?"
    c "¿Objeciones?"

# game/episode018.rpy:412
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_4d7fcdbd:

#   j "Yes, from, and I quote: 'that fat corpse-like browbeater'."
    j "Sí, de, y cito textualmente: \"ese gordo cadáver browbeater\"."

# game/episode018.rpy:413
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_aeea7035:

#   c "So he met my father as well."
    c "Así que también conoció a mi padre."

# game/episode018.rpy:414
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_1d8a3ba5:

#   j "It seems so, yes."
    j "Eso parece, sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:415
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_e5ba6747:

#   c "Does this ship carry Sovereignty clearance codes?"
    c "¿Lleva este barco códigos de autorización de Soberanía?"

# game/episode018.rpy:417
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_130fb281:

#   j "That's the other thing I checked."
    j "Esa es la otra cosa que comprobé."

# game/episode018.rpy:418
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_635bc003:

#   j "It seems that this vessel has clearance on Kvi's authority."
    j "Parece que este buque tiene autorización de Kvi."

# game/episode018.rpy:419
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_c5aed8d5:

#   c "Interesting."
    c "Interesante."

# game/episode018.rpy:420
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_803b9ac6:

#   c "So that means we could fly anywhere."
    c "Eso significa que podríamos volar a cualquier parte."

# game/episode018.rpy:422
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_acfa09bf:

#   j "I assume so, unless we're actually boarded by a Sovereignty patrol."
    j "Supongo que sí, a menos que nos aborde una patrulla de la Soberanía."

# game/episode018.rpy:423
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_4e8c7062:

#   c "Of course."
    c "Por supuesto."

# game/episode018.rpy:424
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_84b02b0d:

#   c "Would it be possible to transfer that clearance to the Bastard?"
    c "¿Sería posible transferir esa autorización al Bastardo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:425
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_a9058f0d:

#   j "Probably, with some effort."
    j "Probablemente, con algo de esfuerzo."

# game/episode018.rpy:427
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_5536127c:

#   j "But the Bastard is probably a well-known ship by now in the Sovereignty."
    j "Pero el Bastardo ya es probablemente un barco muy conocido en el Soberano."

# game/episode018.rpy:428
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_438ebb6e:

#   c "Yes, that's a complication."
    c "Sí, es una complicación."

# game/episode018.rpy:429
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_8380ac5c:

#   c "This ship should be big enough to fit our entire crew though."
    c "Sin embargo, esta nave debería ser lo bastante grande para que quepa toda nuestra tripulación."

# game/episode018.rpy:430
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_12b2a731:

#   j "It's less spacious than the Bastard, but it would indeed fit."
    j "Es menos espacioso que el Bastardo, pero sí cabría."

# game/episode018.rpy:431
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_c57471a1:

#   c "I think we need to share this with the others."
    c "Creo que debemos compartir esto con los demás."

# game/episode018.rpy:432
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_31a08563:

#   c "This might be a way for us to get very close to that Arch on Taagmar."
    c "Esta podría ser una forma de acercarnos a ese Arco en Taagmar."

# game/episode018.rpy:434
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_47acfb9f:

#   "The crew met on the bridge of the Bastard to hear about Jade's discovery and my plan to covertly enter the capital of Taagmar."
    "La tripulación se reunió en el puente del Bastardo para escuchar el descubrimiento de Jade y mi plan de entrar encubiertamente en la capital de Taagmar."

# game/episode018.rpy:435
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_f129ae85:

#   av "If the mercenary ship has that level of Sovereignty clearance, we might just pull this off."
    av "Si la nave mercenaria tiene ese nivel de autorización de Soberanía, podríamos lograrlo."

# game/episode018.rpy:436
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_fc035778:

#   av "But what do we do once we're on Taagmar's surface?"
    av "Pero, ¿qué hacemos una vez en la superficie de Taagmar?"

# game/episode018.rpy:437
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_358acf0e:

#   av "I don't think we'll be able to walk through a warzone to that Arch."
    av "No creo que podamos atravesar una zona de guerra hasta ese Arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:438
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_d831bc73:

#   c "Once we're on the ground, we'll need to get a hold of several Sovereignty armor suits."
    c "Una vez en tierra, necesitaremos hacernos con varios trajes blindados de Soberanía."

# game/episode018.rpy:439
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_5cfc677a:

#   c "Those suits render us anonymous enough to get close to the Arch."
    c "Esos trajes nos dan el anonimato suficiente para acercarnos al Arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:441
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_89c59c93:

#   t "We're going to despoil a battlefield, like common marauders?"
    t "¿Vamos a saquear un campo de batalla, como vulgares merodeadores?"

# game/episode018.rpy:442
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_23a31d67:

#   c "I don't think we have any choice."
    c "No creo que tengamos elección."

# game/episode018.rpy:443
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_0333dd69:

#   c "Sneaking across a battlefield without any disguise seems like a recipe for disaster."
    c "Cruzar a hurtadillas un campo de batalla sin disfraz parece una receta para el desastre."

# game/episode018.rpy:444
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_6518180f:

#   c "At least with the right armor, we can hopefully remain undetected."
    c "Al menos con la armadura adecuada, es de esperar que podamos pasar desapercibidos."

# game/episode018.rpy:446
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_e869cb06:

#   t "Fair enough."
    t "Me parece justo."

# game/episode018.rpy:448
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_35eea777:

#   ce "What about the Bastard?"
    ce "¿Y el Bastardo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:449
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_205bae25:

#   c "We'd have to leave it docked somewhere, for the time being."
    c "Tendríamos que dejarlo atracado en algún sitio, por el momento."

# game/episode018.rpy:450
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_198316df:

#   ce "On Altum Station?"
    ce "¿En la estación de Altum?"

# game/episode018.rpy:451
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_4ce92500:

#   c "I'm not sure if we're that welcome there, considering our exit."
    c "No estoy seguro de que seamos tan bienvenidos allí, teniendo en cuenta nuestra salida."

# game/episode018.rpy:452
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_03c45662:

#   c "We'll leave the ship docked somewhere else."
    c "Dejaremos el barco atracado en otro sitio."

# game/episode018.rpy:454
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_170ec5c3:

#   th "That might be a good opportunity to have some maintenance done."
    th "Esa podría ser una buena oportunidad para hacer algún mantenimiento."

# game/episode018.rpy:455
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_b782adfb:

#   c "Good thinking."
    c "Bien pensado."

# game/episode018.rpy:457
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_4ab4e7b2:

#   l "Is someone going to stay behind with the ship?"
    l "¿Alguien se va a quedar atrás con el barco?"

# game/episode018.rpy:458
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_9d95f2bc:

#   c "I don't think that will be necessary."
    c "No creo que sea necesario."

# game/episode018.rpy:460
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_8bf9f099:

#   na "What about the girl?"
    na "¿Y la chica?"

# game/episode018.rpy:463
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_45fbffe7:

#   c "I think it's time to let her out of the brig."
    c "Creo que es hora de dejarla salir del calabozo."

# game/episode018.rpy:464
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_1f5830fa:

#   na "I still think that's unwise."
    na "Sigo pensando que no es prudente."

# game/episode018.rpy:465
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_8f0df545:

#   c "She'll be under guard and returned to a cell immediately if she tries anything."
    c "Será vigilada y devuelta a una celda inmediatamente si intenta algo."

# game/episode018.rpy:467
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_50babc4a:

#   "My mother remained skeptical, but offered no further objections on the matter."
    "Mi madre permaneció escéptica, pero no puso más objeciones al respecto."

# game/episode018.rpy:469
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_9ddc3d05:

#   "Nadya remained skeptical, but offered no further objections on the matter."
    "Nadya permaneció escéptica, pero no puso más objeciones al respecto."

# game/episode018.rpy:471
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_e574bc7f:

#   c "We'll transfer her over to a cell on Glixken's former ship."
    c "La transferiremos a una celda en la antigua nave de Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:473
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_7c2bf657:

#   "The entire crew was in agreement on the plan to infiltrate Taagmar."
    "Toda la tripulación estaba de acuerdo en el plan para infiltrarse en Taagmar."

# game/episode018.rpy:474
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_5724d004:

#   "Thyia had selected a suitable station to leave the Bastard docked for repairs."
    "Thyia había seleccionado una estación adecuada para dejar el Bastardo atracado para reparaciones."

# game/episode018.rpy:475
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_c7059781:

#   "From there we would travel back to the battlefield created by the Sovereignty and try to land Glixken's ship near the capital."
    "Desde allí viajaríamos de vuelta al campo de batalla creado por el Soberano e intentaríamos desembarcar la nave de Glixken cerca de la capital."

# game/episode018.rpy:476
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_26668c95:

#   "With Glixken’s ship, helmed by Kit and a skeleton crew, following close, we headed towards the station."
    "Con la nave de Glixken, timoneada por Kit y una tripulación esquelética, siguiéndonos de cerca, nos dirigimos hacia la estación."

# game/episode018.rpy:477
translate spanish ep018_desert_exit_c6709057:

#   "It would take us a few hours to reach it and make our way back to Taagmar."
    "Tardaríamos unas horas en llegar y regresar a Taagmar."

# game/episode018.rpy:522
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_ed32d793:

#   "The space station turned out to be a small base, but equipped for all the necessary repairs and maintenance."
    "La estación espacial resultó ser una base pequeña, pero equipada para todas las reparaciones y el mantenimiento necesarios."

# game/episode018.rpy:523
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_f0db8658:

#   "Thyia and Céline haggled with the dockmaster over a suitable price, and joined us later on Glixken's ship."
    "Thyia y Céline regatearon con el dueño del muelle un precio adecuado y se unieron a nosotros más tarde en el barco de Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:525
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_87df7d34:

#   "The trip to Taagmar wouldn't take very long, due to the conveniently placed gateway near the space station, that would put us very near our destination."
    "El viaje a Taagmar no llevaría mucho tiempo, debido a la conveniente ubicación del portal cerca de la estación espacial, que nos situaría muy cerca de nuestro destino."

# game/episode018.rpy:527
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e76cba35:

#   "Before long, we were nearing the outer perimeter of the fleet occupying Taagmar."
    "En poco tiempo, nos acercábamos al perímetro exterior de la flota que ocupaba Taagmar."

# game/episode018.rpy:528
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_19a49da0:

#   "Patrols could ask for our credentials at any step of the way and I just hoped Glixken's clearance would get us through."
    "Las patrullas podían pedirnos nuestras credenciales en cualquier momento y yo sólo esperaba que la autorización de Glixken nos permitiera pasar."

# game/episode018.rpy:530
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_a436781f:

#   ce "We're at the point of no return."
    ce "Estamos en un punto sin retorno."

# game/episode018.rpy:531
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_6db2701e:

#   c "Take us in."
    c "Llévanos dentro."

# game/episode018.rpy:533
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_6cc9519a:

#   "We passed the dotted line projected on the navigation screen and set a course for the capital."
    "Pasamos la línea de puntos proyectada en la pantalla de navegación y ponemos rumbo a la capital."

# game/episode018.rpy:534
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_835ad31c:

#   ce "We're being scanned."
    ce "Nos están escaneando."

# game/episode018.rpy:536
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_ed063c4d:

#   "Everyone present on the bridge held their breath."
    "Todos los presentes en el puente contuvieron la respiración."

# game/episode018.rpy:537
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_08f29b3b:

#   "If a patrol were to hail us, we'd have to bluff our way through over the radio, and I just didn't know how convincing my impression of Glixken's grating voice would be."
    "Si nos llamaba una patrulla, tendríamos que hablar por radio, y no sabía hasta qué punto sería convincente mi impresión de la voz chirriante de Glixken."

# game/episode018.rpy:538
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_58d76297:

#   "Thankfully, the comm didn't crackle for the duration of our trek through Sovereignty lines and subsequent descent towards the planet's surface."
    "Afortunadamente, las comunicaciones no se interrumpieron durante nuestro viaje a través de las líneas de soberanía y el posterior descenso hacia la superficie del planeta."

# game/episode018.rpy:540
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_25bbdc80:

#   ce "We're through."
    ce "Hemos terminado."

# game/episode018.rpy:542
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e40acde2:

#   "Our ship punched through Taagmar's cloud deck and revealed the battle-scarred terrain below."
    "Nuestra nave atravesó la cubierta de nubes de Taagmar y reveló el terreno lleno de cicatrices de batalla que había debajo."

# game/episode018.rpy:543
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_ae3d0039:

#   "Frequent explosions dotted the landscape, indicating battle zones."
    "Frecuentes explosiones salpicaban el paisaje, indicando zonas de batalla."

# game/episode018.rpy:544
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_0847a868:

#   "One of those zones was our destination and we kept speeding towards that point without interruption."
    "Una de esas zonas era nuestro destino y seguimos acelerando hacia ese punto sin interrupción."

# game/episode018.rpy:546
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_42c9433b:

#   ce "I'm putting us down in two minutes."
    ce "Nos bajo en dos minutos."

# game/episode018.rpy:547
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_7963cf59:

#   c "Understood."
    c "Entendido."

# game/episode018.rpy:549
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e819cfd1:

#   "Our landing place was located in an industrial district of the capital."
    "Nuestro lugar de aterrizaje estaba situado en un distrito industrial de la capital."

# game/episode018.rpy:550
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_21dba89e:

#   "According to the maps in the ship's computer, it was near the Arch, but not too near to the front of the Sovereignty assault."
    "Según los mapas del ordenador de la nave, estaba cerca del Arco, pero no demasiado cerca del frente de asalto del Soberano."

# game/episode018.rpy:552
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_941517ea:

#   c "Is that the Arch?"
    c "¿Es el Arco?"

# game/episode018.rpy:553
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_710abf60:

#   ce "Must be, yes, too much activity going on around there for it not to be."
    ce "Debe de haber, sí, demasiada actividad por allí como para que no la haya."

# game/episode018.rpy:555
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_8d492062:

#   "Céline landed between the ruined towers of a large factory."
    "Céline aterrizó entre las torres en ruinas de una gran fábrica."

# game/episode018.rpy:557
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_89ceff89:

#   c "Right, let's see if we can scavenge some Sovereignty armor and weapons."
    c "Bien, veamos si podemos recoger algunas armas y armaduras de Soberanía."

# game/episode018.rpy:558
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_a2a48d79:

#   "There had evidently been heavy fighting near the factory."
    "Evidentemente había habido fuertes combates cerca de la fábrica."

# game/episode018.rpy:560
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_ac652920:

#   "Several Taagmar bodies were strewn across the perimeter."
    "Varios cuerpos de Taagmar estaban esparcidos por el perímetro."

# game/episode018.rpy:561
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_816286ec:

#   "Most of the Taagmar were killed by Sovereignty energy weapons."
    "La mayoría de los Taagmar fueron asesinados por armas de energía del Soberano."

# game/episode018.rpy:563
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e0e1517d:

#   "I was about to give up hope of finding a Sovereignty soldier, when I spotted the tell-tale redness of a Sovereignty helmet visor."
    "Estaba a punto de perder la esperanza de encontrar a un soldado del Soberano, cuando vi el enrojecimiento revelador de la visera de un casco del Soberano."

# game/episode018.rpy:564
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_8db4ede1:

#   c "Found one."
    c "Encontré uno."

# game/episode018.rpy:566
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_eaf4b619:

#   av "Me too."
    av "A mí también."

# game/episode018.rpy:567
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_fd930087:

#   zi "Doesn't either side retrieve their fallen soldiers?"
    zi "¿Ningún bando recupera a sus soldados caídos?"

# game/episode018.rpy:569
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_1cdd3e4a:

#   c "The Sovereignty will, in time, if they care enough."
    c "La Soberanía lo hará, con el tiempo, si se preocupa lo suficiente."

# game/episode018.rpy:570
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_a2357a85:

#   c "As for the Taagmar, I'm not sure if there are enough fighters left to take care of their dead."
    c "En cuanto a los Taagmar, no estoy seguro de que queden suficientes combatientes para ocuparse de sus muertos."

# game/episode018.rpy:572
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_37cb4a24:

#   "Working in silence, we didn't have to venture out too far from the place where we landed to find enough pieces of armor and weaponry."
    "Trabajando en silencio, no tuvimos que aventurarnos demasiado lejos del lugar donde desembarcamos para encontrar suficientes piezas de armadura y armamento."

# game/episode018.rpy:573
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_cc7b3893:

#   "The nano-material of the armor would conform to any type of body, so we didn't have to worry about dress sizes."
    "El nanomaterial de la armadura se adaptaba a cualquier tipo de cuerpo, así que no teníamos que preocuparnos por las tallas de los vestidos."

# game/episode018.rpy:574
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_2bb5869c:

#   "While the amount of fallen Taagmar soldiers was easily triple that of Sovereignty casualties, there were a great number of bodies to be found."
    "Aunque la cantidad de soldados de Taagmar caídos era fácilmente el triple que la de bajas de la Soberanía, había un gran número de cadáveres por encontrar."

# game/episode018.rpy:576
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_95426a48:

#   "It seemed the Taagmar had put up a costly, albeit doomed defense against their invaders."
    "Parecía que los Taagmar habían planteado una defensa costosa, aunque condenada al fracaso, contra sus invasores."

# game/episode018.rpy:577
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_664bf969:

#   "Back at the ship, we cleaned the armor suits as best we could and then donned them."
    "De vuelta a la nave, limpiamos los trajes blindados lo mejor que pudimos y luego nos los pusimos."

# game/episode018.rpy:579
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_44379a11:

#   ki "Is it safe to leave the ship here?"
    ki "¿Es seguro dejar la nave aquí?"

# game/episode018.rpy:580
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_81433129:

#   c "I don't think any place here in the capital can be considered safe."
    c "No creo que ningún lugar de la capital pueda considerarse seguro."

# game/episode018.rpy:581
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_15e7a180:

#   c "But the fighting has died down considerably and this ring of the city doesn't seem to be contested anymore by either side."
    c "Pero los combates se han calmado considerablemente y este anillo de la ciudad ya no parece disputado por ninguno de los dos bandos."

# game/episode018.rpy:583
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_99ffdc55:

#   th "The Sovereignty will probably leave the ship alone anyway, considering the credentials it bears."
    th "De todas formas, el Soberano probablemente dejará la nave en paz, teniendo en cuenta las credenciales que lleva."

# game/episode018.rpy:585
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b9bd2ac0:

#   ki "Right, into the fray then?"
    ki "Bien, ¿a la lucha entonces?"

# game/episode018.rpy:587
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_7db78bff:

#   j "What if we encounter resistance?"
    j "¿Y si encontramos resistencia?"

# game/episode018.rpy:588
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_0aa3b9c4:

#   c "Our aim is to prevent any encounters."
    c "Nuestro objetivo es evitar cualquier encuentro."

# game/episode018.rpy:589
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_712415dd:

#   c "But if we run into the Taagmar, we'd have to return fire, I'm afraid."
    c "Pero si nos encontramos con el Taagmar, tendríamos que devolver el fuego, me temo."

# game/episode018.rpy:590
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_cc9d9100:

#   c "We'll do anything to prevent us from killing Taagmar, but if it's them or us, we choose the latter."
    c "Haremos lo que sea para evitar matar a Taagmar, pero si son ellos o nosotros, elegimos lo segundo."

# game/episode018.rpy:591
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_6ac6febd:

#   c "The Sovereignty troops shouldn't give us trouble on account of our disguises."
    c "Las tropas del Soberano no deberían darnos problemas a causa de nuestros disfraces."

# game/episode018.rpy:592
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e134e21a:

#   c "If they do, we deal with them quietly and permanently."
    c "Si lo hacen, nos ocupamos de ellos de forma discreta y permanente."

# game/episode018.rpy:594
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_69c9a036:

#   "Everybody voiced their approval and we headed out towards the gateway."
    "Todos expresaron su aprobación y nos dirigimos hacia el portal."

# game/episode018.rpy:596
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_3f307b22:

#   "Fighting could be heard in the distance, as we approached the Arch."
    "Se oían combates a lo lejos, mientras nos acercábamos al Arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:597
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_2cb18ebf:

#   "The further we got near the structure, the more impressive it became."
    "Cuanto más nos acercábamos a la estructura, más impresionante resultaba."

# game/episode018.rpy:599
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_27035a13:

#   "The gateway towered over all the buildings the Taagmar had built around it."
    "La puerta se alzaba sobre todos los edificios que los Taagmar habían construido a su alrededor."

# game/episode018.rpy:601
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_bc9aadcb:

#   "The streets we had to cross were empty, except for the Taagmar casualties and an occasional lifeless Sovereignty body."
    "Las calles que teníamos que cruzar estaban vacías, salvo por las bajas de Taagmar y algún que otro cuerpo sin vida del Soberano."

# game/episode018.rpy:602
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_4c164908:

#   "Continuous gunfire could be heard, but on the other side of the city, the Sovereignty apparently encountered more resistance."
    "Se oían continuos disparos, pero al otro lado de la ciudad, el Soberano aparentemente encontró más resistencia."

# game/episode018.rpy:603
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_f3f10577:

#   "Thankfully, we didn't have to shoot anyone, Taagmar or otherwise."
    "Afortunadamente, no tuvimos que disparar a nadie, Taagmar o no."

# game/episode018.rpy:605
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_8a1f0523:

#   "As we neared the base of the Arch, several Sovereignty barricades could be seen in the distance."
    "A medida que nos acercábamos a la base del Arco, se divisaban a lo lejos varias barricadas de Soberanía."

# game/episode018.rpy:607
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_892f07bd:

#   c "We're going to march double time through those barricades."
    c "Vamos a marchar a paso ligero a través de esas barricadas."

# game/episode018.rpy:608
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b77fe5c0:

#   c "Just a small squad, returning to base..."
    c "Sólo un pequeño escuadrón, regresando a la base..."

# game/episode018.rpy:609
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_cdfb27fa:

#   ki "What if we're stopped by some officer?"
    ki "¿Y si nos para algún agente?"

# game/episode018.rpy:610
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_9b6729a2:

#   c "We'll bluff our way out if it."
    c "Nos echaremos un farol."

# game/episode018.rpy:611
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_2c033a13:

#   c "If that doesn't work, aim for the head."
    c "Si eso no funciona, apunta a la cabeza."

# game/episode018.rpy:612
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_c1dd1b6e:

#   ki "Gotcha."
    ki "Entendido."

# game/episode018.rpy:614
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_d6d69a19:

#   "We ran towards the barricades, attempting to display some measure of military discipline."
    "Corrimos hacia las barricadas, intentando mostrar cierta disciplina militar."

# game/episode018.rpy:616
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_f3f5756d:

#   "The soldiers manning the barricades evidently didn't care and waved us through."
    "A los soldados que vigilaban las barricadas no les importó y nos hicieron pasar."

# game/episode018.rpy:617
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_d8e8d264:

#   "From this point, all roads led towards the base of the Arch, so without breaking our stride, we continued on."
    "Desde este punto, todos los caminos llevaban hacia la base del Arco, así que sin romper el paso, seguimos adelante."

# game/episode018.rpy:618
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_d6d96ac2:

#   "Several other squads were making their way towards the Arch as well."
    "Otros escuadrones también se dirigían hacia el Arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:620
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_60734496:

#   "The reason why became clear when we reached the base of the structure."
    "El motivo quedó claro cuando llegamos a la base de la estructura."

# game/episode018.rpy:621
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_bcfd143d:

#   "An armored vehicle had just parked and soldiers were forming a protective corridor for the passengers coming out of the back."
    "Un vehículo blindado acababa de aparcar y los soldados formaban un pasillo de protección para los pasajeros que salían de la parte trasera."

# game/episode018.rpy:623
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_bf985823:

#   l "Who is that guy?"
    l "¿Quién es ese tipo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:624
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_705ba921:

#   c "The sickly grandpa, Erylin's new boyfriend?"
    c "¿El abuelo enfermizo, el nuevo novio de Erylin?"

# game/episode018.rpy:626
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_0f09edec:

#   ve "It's the Confessor."
    ve "Es la Confesora."

# game/episode018.rpy:628
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_31f89f35:

#   c "I reckon that’s the Confessor, Erylin obviously made a deal with him before betraying the Acarhyn."
    c "Creo que es la Confesora, Erylin obviamente hizo un trato con él antes de traicionar a los Acarhyn."

# game/episode018.rpy:630
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_296250e3:

#   e "And they’re now both working for the Sovereignty?"
    e "¿Y ahora ambos trabajan para la Soberanía?"

# game/episode018.rpy:631
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b1cff47c:

#   c "Yes, it seems daddy-dear made some new friends..."
    c "Sí, parece que papá Oreja hizo nuevos amigos..."

# game/episode018.rpy:632
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_d5144574:

#   c "Though it might just be a marriage of convenience."
    c "Aunque podría ser sólo un matrimonio de conveniencia."

# game/episode018.rpy:634
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_14101c91:

#   ki "I guess they’re not just here for the sights?"
    ki "¿Supongo que no están aquí sólo por las vistas?"

# game/episode018.rpy:635
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_866a72dd:

#   c "A planet-wide invasion and genocide just to visit a landmark seems a little excessive, even for the Sovereignty."
    c "Una invasión de todo el planeta y un genocidio sólo para visitar un punto de referencia parece un poco excesivo, incluso para la Soberanía."

# game/episode018.rpy:637
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e6b31aef:

#   ve "The Confessor is probably going to activate the gateway."
    ve "La Confesora probablemente activará el portal."

# game/episode018.rpy:639
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_d054e44d:

#   ki "It looks like they’re trying to open the gateway."
    ki "Parece que están intentando abrir el portal."

# game/episode018.rpy:640
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e1aab1ef:

#   c "Let’s make sure we’ll be among the first to march through once he gets it open."
    c "Asegurémonos de ser de los primeros en pasar una vez que lo abra."

# game/episode018.rpy:645
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_9e80ab5d:

#   "We joined a contingent of soldiers near the foundation of the arch."
    "Nos unimos a un contingente de soldados cerca de los cimientos del arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:646
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_647cb451:

#   "The Confessor was standing right in front of the Arch, the others keeping their distance."
    "La Confesora estaba de pie justo delante del Arco, los demás mantenían las distancias."

# game/episode018.rpy:647
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_a6f23057:

#   "He had his arms raised towards the structure and looked to be concentrating on something."
    "Tenía los brazos levantados hacia la estructura y parecía concentrado en algo."

# game/episode018.rpy:649
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_3c0d16bb:

#   c "He looks like a stage magician who’s trying too hard."
    c "Parece un mago que se esfuerza demasiado."

# game/episode018.rpy:652
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e94474a6:

#   ve "You’re not too far off the mark."
    ve "No vas muy desencaminado."

# game/episode018.rpy:653
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_eec6d6c5:

#   ve "The Confessor relies on varied tricks to enhance his mystique."
    ve "La Confesora recurre a diversos trucos para realzar su mística."

# game/episode018.rpy:654
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_39efbe1a:

#   c "You’ve got to be kidding me..."
    c "Tienes que estar bromeando..."

# game/episode018.rpy:655
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_60f0ec8b:

#   ki "Looks mightily impressive though."
    ki "Pero tiene un aspecto impresionante."

# game/episode018.rpy:656
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_7428ad0e:

#   c "They should have brought a fan to make his cape billow dramatically."
    c "Deberían haber traído un ventilador para que su capa ondeara espectacularmente."

# game/episode018.rpy:657
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_ef8f5d84:

#   "Aven nudged me in the side."
    "Aven me dio un codazo en el costado."

# game/episode018.rpy:658
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_875c3f88:

#   av "Look over there."
    av "Mira allí."

# game/episode018.rpy:660
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b0f8f97d:

#   "Several of the Confessor’s handmaidens were positioned at both sides of the arch."
    "Varias siervas de la Confesora se situaron a ambos lados del arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:661
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_130cf3cf:

#   "They appeared to be standing guard, but some of them were fiddling with something near the base of the monument."
    "Parecían estar montando guardia, pero algunos jugueteaban con algo cerca de la base del monumento."

# game/episode018.rpy:663
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_023bcd8d:

#   "Their work was mostly obscured by the other handmaidens standing guard and everyone else was looking at the theatrics the Confessor was performing in front of the Arch."
    "Su trabajo estaba casi oculto por las otras siervas que montaban guardia y todos los demás miraban el teatro que la Confesora representaba delante del Arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:664
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b4f91e89:

#   av "I think they’re pressing on the stones, inputting some kind of key code."
    av "Creo que están presionando las piedras, introduciendo algún tipo de código clave."

# game/episode018.rpy:665
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_bfc84a27:

#   c "Interesting, it seems that the Confessor doesn’t want everyone to know about this ancient keypad."
    c "Interesante, parece que la Confesora no quiere que todos sepan de este antiguo teclado."

# game/episode018.rpy:667
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e34a7ea7:

#   "The Confessor’s hands shot out towards the gateway and a stream of energy seemingly flowed from his hands."
    "Las manos de la Confesora salieron disparadas hacia el portal y una corriente de energía fluyó aparentemente de sus manos."

# game/episode018.rpy:669
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_de1e3ce5:

#   "The air inside the Arch rippled and twisted until the view of the Taagmar city disappeared, replaced by a different landscape altogether."
    "El aire del interior del Arco onduló y se retorció hasta que la vista de la ciudad de Taagmar desapareció, sustituida por un paisaje totalmente distinto."

# game/episode018.rpy:670
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_42d4e3fa:

#   na "He did it."
    na "Lo consiguió."

# game/episode018.rpy:671
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_694a6295:

#   av "Well, his handmaidens did it, to be more accurate."
    av "Bueno, sus siervas lo hicieron, para ser más exactos."

# game/episode018.rpy:673
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e5e7c780:

#   "Some orders were shouted and a squad of Sovereignty soldiers moved forward, followed by several handmaidens."
    "Se gritaron algunas órdenes y un pelotón de soldados del Soberano avanzó, seguido de varias siervas."

# game/episode018.rpy:674
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_36404008:

#   "They were clearly intended to be the vanguard of this expedition."
    "Estaban claramente destinados a ser la vanguardia de esta expedición."

# game/episode018.rpy:675
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_065c571f:

#   "The soldiers passed through the gate into the foreign landscape."
    "Los soldados atravesaron la puerta y se adentraron en el paisaje extranjero."

# game/episode018.rpy:677
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_2256d8ff:

#   "When they gave the all-clear after a few minutes, the entire column of Sovereignty troops came in motion."
    "Cuando dieron el visto bueno al cabo de unos minutos, toda la columna de tropas de la Soberanía se puso en marcha."

# game/episode018.rpy:678
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_7c3e56e4:

#   "The Confessor and the others got into the armored vehicle again and they drove through the gateway, soldiers trailing behind them."
    "La Confesora y los demás volvieron a subir al vehículo blindado y atravesaron el portal, con los soldados detrás."

# game/episode018.rpy:679
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_ccd72f8e:

#   "The squad we joined was also about to go through the Arch."
    "El escuadrón al que nos unimos también estaba a punto de pasar por el Arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:681
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_600fd026:

#   "The passage to the other world was almost unnoticeable."
    "El paso al otro mundo era casi imperceptible."

# game/episode018.rpy:683
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_f56b369a:

#   "One moment we were on the Taagmar homeworld and the next we were somewhere else entirely."
    "En un momento estábamos en el mundo de Taagmar y al siguiente en otro lugar."

# game/episode018.rpy:684
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_85ac3409:

#   "Judging by the sky, we weren’t even on the same planet anymore."
    "A juzgar por el cielo, ya ni siquiera estábamos en el mismo planeta."

# game/episode018.rpy:686
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_de5a695c:

#   "A sandy plain stretched out before us, high rocky peaks visible in the distance."
    "Ante nosotros se extendía una llanura arenosa, con altas cumbres rocosas visibles en la distancia."

# game/episode018.rpy:688
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_8461512b:

#   "We’d exited a gateway similar to the Arch on Taagmar, but it wasn’t the only structure in the vicinity, as several ruins could be made out."
    "Habíamos salido de un portal similar al Arco de Taagmar, pero no era la única estructura en las inmediaciones, ya que se distinguían varias ruinas."

# game/episode018.rpy:690
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_9757d650:

#   "The armored vehicle containing the VIPs was speeding towards a very specific location however."
    "Sin embargo, el vehículo blindado que contenía a los VIP se dirigía a toda velocidad hacia un lugar muy concreto."

# game/episode018.rpy:691
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_faf91123:

#   "An imposing building stood a few miles from the Arch."
    "Un imponente edificio se alzaba a pocos kilómetros del Arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:693
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_53ad8ee8:

#   "It looked ancient when we neared it, but it wasn’t a ruin like the ones on the horizon."
    "Parecía antigua cuando nos acercamos a ella, pero no era una ruina como las del horizonte."

# game/episode018.rpy:695
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_d9162e13:

#   ki "Looks like a temple."
    ki "Parece un templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:696
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_63cb1300:

#   av "What are we going to do, split?"
    av "¿Qué vamos a hacer, dividirnos?"

# game/episode018.rpy:697
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_d382f12b:

#   c "Not yet, it would attract too much attention and I really want to know what’s inside that temple."
    c "Todavía no, llamaría demasiado la atención y realmente quiero saber qué hay dentro de ese templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:699
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_243aca14:

#   "The column stopped at the large doors at the front of the temple, the people inside the armored vehicle disembarked once more."
    "La columna se detuvo ante las grandes puertas de la parte delantera del templo, y las personas que se encontraban en el interior del vehículo blindado volvieron a apearse."

# game/episode018.rpy:701
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_61596aec:

#   "The Confessor made some dramatic gestures which spurred his Handmaidens into action."
    "La Confesora hizo algunos gestos dramáticos que incitaron a sus Siervas a entrar en acción."

# game/episode018.rpy:703
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_280b6a5d:

#   "The four of them pushed against one of the large doors."
    "Los cuatro se empujaron contra una de las grandes puertas."

# game/episode018.rpy:708
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b24d9421:

#   "With some effort, but not as much as you’d expect from a heavy stone door supposedly shut for centuries, they managed to open the door."
    "Con algo de esfuerzo, pero no tanto como cabría esperar de una pesada puerta de piedra supuestamente cerrada durante siglos, consiguieron abrirla."

# game/episode018.rpy:709
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_c962ea6a:

#   "A recon squad entered the temple first and apparently found nothing dangerous, because the Confessor and his party ventured in not long after."
    "Un escuadrón de reconocimiento entró primero en el templo y aparentemente no encontró nada peligroso, porque la Confesora y su grupo se aventuraron a entrar no mucho después."

# game/episode018.rpy:711
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_dc571528:

#   "The temple was vast inside, all large stone stairs and high domed ceilings."
    "El templo era inmenso por dentro, todo grandes escaleras de piedra y altos techos abovedados."

# game/episode018.rpy:712
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_3fcdd09a:

#   "The stonecutting involved was basic, but of an elegance that exhumed a certain class in itself, even under the many layers of dust."
    "La cantería era básica, pero de una elegancia que exhalaba cierta clase en sí misma, incluso bajo las muchas capas de polvo."

# game/episode018.rpy:714
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_f02d9114:

#   "The Confessor already stood before another set of double doors, evidently thinking the same trick he performed outside would work here again."
    "La Confesora ya estaba ante otro par de puertas dobles, evidentemente pensando que el mismo truco que realizó fuera funcionaría aquí de nuevo."

# game/episode018.rpy:715
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_1d3591a1:

#   "However, the Handmaidens pushed against the door in vain and it wouldn’t even budge when a couple of Sovereignty soldiers joined in to help."
    "Sin embargo, las Siervas empujaron la puerta en vano y ni siquiera cedió cuando un par de soldados de la Soberanía se unieron para ayudar."

# game/episode018.rpy:717
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_62f5e615:

#   ag "This is clearly not going to work."
    ag "Está claro que esto no va a funcionar."

# game/episode018.rpy:718
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_4ca34703:

#   ag "With the gate remaining open, I’ll have my men bring in the excavation gear."
    ag "Con la puerta abierta, haré que mis hombres traigan el equipo de excavación."

# game/episode018.rpy:719
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b7b6c762:

#   ag "I’m sure explosives will do the trick nicely."
    ag "Estoy seguro de que los explosivos harán el truco muy bien."

# game/episode018.rpy:720
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e6fcd7fe:

#   er "Only if you want to collapse the roof on top of us, and destroy the Key that is inside this chamber."
    er "Sólo si quieres derrumbar el techo sobre nosotros, y destruir la Llave que está dentro de esta cámara."

# game/episode018.rpy:721
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_8144c204:

#   ag "We’ll do it the hard way then."
    ag "Entonces lo haremos por las malas."

# game/episode018.rpy:723
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_8fb4aeba:

#   "My father conveyed his wishes to one of the officers standing nearby."
    "Mi padre transmitió sus deseos a uno de los oficiales que estaban cerca."

# game/episode018.rpy:725
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_aa675115:

#   man "Sir, I must inform you that a dust storm has struck up outside, limiting our visibility."
    man "Señor, debo informarle de que se ha desatado una tormenta de polvo en el exterior que limita nuestra visibilidad."

# game/episode018.rpy:726
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_af89593e:

#   ag "So?"
    ag "¿Y?"

# game/episode018.rpy:727
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_87b891a2:

#   ag "I’m sure your men can find their way back to the Arch through a little dust."
    ag "Estoy seguro de que tus hombres pueden encontrar el camino de vuelta al Arco con un poco de polvo."

# game/episode018.rpy:728
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_ecc12aaa:

#   ag "Time is of the essence, move!"
    ag "El tiempo apremia, ¡muévete!"

# game/episode018.rpy:730
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_38edd898:

#   "The officer knew better than to argue and proceeded to bark orders to every soldier assembled."
    "El oficial sabía que no debía discutir y procedió a ladrar órdenes a todos los soldados reunidos."

# game/episode018.rpy:732
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_c923ce1e:

#   c "I think we’ve seen enough, let’s use this moment to slip out and find some cover."
    c "Creo que ya hemos visto suficiente, aprovechemos este momento para escabullirnos y buscar algo de cobertura."

# game/episode018.rpy:733
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_1a92b721:

#   "Everyone was running around, acting on the orders the officer had given them."
    "Todos corrían de un lado a otro, siguiendo las órdenes del oficial."

# game/episode018.rpy:735
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_010bbb84:

#   "Several men marched back to the gateway, to retrieve excavation equipment, while others proceeded to set up a base camp inside the temple."
    "Varios hombres regresaron a la entrada para recoger el equipo de excavación, mientras otros instalaban un campamento base en el interior del templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:736
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_e77169a4:

#   "We marched together with a squad heading out to the Arch."
    "Marchamos juntos con un pelotón hacia el Arco."

# game/episode018.rpy:738
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_91ced2fd:

#   "The dust storm outside wasn’t as bad as I feared, but it did limit visibility considerably, something we could use to our advantage."
    "La tormenta de polvo en el exterior no era tan mala como me temía, pero limitaba considerablemente la visibilidad, algo que podíamos aprovechar a nuestro favor."

# game/episode018.rpy:739
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_22ecbc9f:

#   "We gradually increased our distance to the tail end of the squad and broke away after the last soldier was out of view."
    "Aumentamos gradualmente nuestra distancia hasta la cola del pelotón y nos separamos después de que el último soldado se perdiera de vista."

# game/episode018.rpy:740
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_53bd2f7e:

#   "With the temple at our backs, we had some inkling of our bearings."
    "Con el templo a nuestras espaldas, pudimos orientarnos un poco."

# game/episode018.rpy:741
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b8f50884:

#   "I decided to head towards the ruins we saw earlier in the distance."
    "Decidí dirigirme hacia las ruinas que vimos antes en la distancia."

# game/episode018.rpy:743
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_fc4362cf:

#   "As the dust storm began to clear somewhat, we reached the ruins."
    "Cuando la tormenta de polvo empezó a despejarse un poco, llegamos a las ruinas."

# game/episode018.rpy:745
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_951dd895:

#   c "This place should give us a good view of the comings and goings to the temple."
    c "Este lugar debería darnos una buena vista de las idas y venidas al templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:746
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_be2310b8:

#   e "How long before they break through that door?"
    e "¿Cuánto tardarán en atravesar esa puerta?"

# game/episode018.rpy:747
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_4027ce0d:

#   na "I think it may be a while, if Agust doesn’t get his way and blows the place up."
    na "Creo que puede pasar un tiempo, si Agust no se sale con la suya y vuela todo por los aires."

# game/episode018.rpy:749
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_311dd2a5:

#   l "Wouldn’t it have been better to stay inside the temple?"
    l "¿No habría sido mejor quedarse dentro del templo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:750
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_0643a147:

#   c "I’m not sure how long our disguises would have held up, or we could have been sent back to Taagmar for some reason."
    c "No estoy seguro de cuánto tiempo habrían aguantado nuestros disfraces, o podríamos haber sido enviados de vuelta a Taagmar por alguna razón."

# game/episode018.rpy:751
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_66107a33:

#   c "But we’ll need to go back and see how much progress they’ve made."
    c "Pero tendremos que volver atrás y ver cuánto han progresado."

# game/episode018.rpy:752
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_d046694a:

#   l "And then what?"
    l "¿Y después qué?"

# game/episode018.rpy:753
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_7e235a27:

#   c "Erylin mentioned a Key."
    c "Erylin mencionó una Llave."

# game/episode018.rpy:754
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_cf064cf7:

#   c "I think that Key is something we need to get our hands on."
    c "Creo que esa Llave es algo a lo que tenemos que echar mano."

# game/episode018.rpy:756
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_42f342f8:

#   av "Let’s hope the Key isn’t as big as everything else in that temple, otherwise we’d need a truck to transport it."
    av "Esperemos que la Llave no sea tan grande como todo lo que hay en ese templo, de lo contrario necesitaríamos un camión para transportarla."

# game/episode018.rpy:757
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_b8fb687e:

#   c "The Sovereignty didn’t immediately bring the heavy gear to the temple, so I think they aren’t expecting the Key to be that big, whatever it is."
    c "El Soberano no llevó inmediatamente el equipo pesado al templo, así que creo que no esperan que la Llave sea tan grande, sea lo que sea."

# game/episode018.rpy:758
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_1c10aa7e:

#   c "Anyway, we should make camp and figure out a schedule to keep watch on the temple."
    c "De todos modos, deberíamos acampar y establecer un horario para vigilar el templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:760
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_f0cdb8e0:

#   "During our exit from the temple, Kit had the bright idea to grab a bag of supplies from the heavy transport."
    "Durante nuestra salida del templo, Kit tuvo la brillante idea de coger una bolsa de provisiones del pesado transporte."

# game/episode018.rpy:761
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_24e91c98:

#   "We used the supplies he took to set up camp and explored the ruins."
    "Con las provisiones que se llevó montamos el campamento y exploramos las ruinas."

# game/episode018.rpy:762
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_567aed53:

#   "Luckily, not everything was reduced to rubble, some structures still stood, or at least partly."
    "Por suerte, no todo quedó reducido a escombros, algunas estructuras seguían en pie, o al menos en parte."

# game/episode018.rpy:763
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_698631b1:

#   "We found a small square with several small adjoining buildings."
    "Encontramos una pequeña plaza con varios edificios pequeños contiguos."

# game/episode018.rpy:765
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_29ec0b1f:

#   "The position sheltered us from anyone passing by and it was relatively defensible."
    "La posición nos protegía de cualquiera que pasara y era relativamente defendible."

# game/episode018.rpy:766
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_243a2a41:

#   "We divided our sleeping bags over the buildings and decided the guard duty order during the day."
    "Nos repartimos los sacos de dormir por los edificios y decidimos el orden de guardia durante el día."

# game/episode018.rpy:767
translate spanish ep018_taagmar_ed7c7264:

#   "Then, all we had to do was wait."
    "Entonces, todo lo que teníamos que hacer era esperar."

# game/episode018.rpy:775
translate spanish ep018_temple_43177dc6:

#   "There was a lot of activity in and around the temple the following days."
    "Los días siguientes hubo mucha actividad en el templo y sus alrededores."

# game/episode018.rpy:776
translate spanish ep018_temple_01310b79:

#   "On the second day, heavy machinery was brought through the gateway and into the temple."
    "El segundo día, se introdujo maquinaria pesada por el portal hasta el interior del templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:777
translate spanish ep018_temple_22bafb0f:

#   "The gateway was open day and night and guarded at all times."
    "La puerta estaba abierta día y noche y vigilada en todo momento."

# game/episode018.rpy:779
translate spanish ep018_temple_ee0d733b:

#   "More heavy equipment kept pouring in the next day, indicating a distinct lack of progress breaching the door."
    "Al día siguiente siguieron llegando más equipos pesados, lo que indicaba una clara falta de progreso en la apertura de la puerta."

# game/episode018.rpy:780
translate spanish ep018_temple_3a98ce71:

#   "The armored vehicle containing my father and his allies had left on the first day and didn’t return."
    "El vehículo blindado que contenía a mi padre y a sus aliados había partido el primer día y no regresó."

# game/episode018.rpy:781
translate spanish ep018_temple_37a3f2ef:

#   "They were probably waiting on the good news somewhere cozy high above the rubble that once was Taagmar."
    "Probablemente estaban esperando las buenas noticias en algún lugar acogedor por encima de los escombros que una vez fue Taagmar."

# game/episode018.rpy:783
translate spanish ep018_temple_fc099217:

#   "After four days, we noticed the armored vehicle speeding towards the temple, followed by a contingent of soldiers."
    "Al cabo de cuatro días, vimos que el vehículo blindado se dirigía a toda velocidad hacia el templo, seguido por un contingente de soldados."

# game/episode018.rpy:784
translate spanish ep018_temple_e0403681:

#   "The excavation team must have had some success opening the doors, or my father had become bored and just wanted to needle his minions."
    "El equipo de excavación debía de haber conseguido abrir las puertas, o mi padre se había aburrido y sólo quería aguijonear a sus secuaces."

# game/episode018.rpy:785
translate spanish ep018_temple_91c73756:

#   "Either way we had to check out the situation."
    "En cualquier caso, teníamos que comprobar la situación."

# game/episode018.rpy:787
translate spanish ep018_temple_7c293790:

#   "The crew quickly assembled all the sleeping gear and after a few minutes we crossed the plain towards the temple."
    "La tripulación montó rápidamente todo el equipo para dormir y al cabo de unos minutos cruzamos la llanura en dirección al templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:788
translate spanish ep018_temple_6bf931c8:

#   "We made sure we weren’t seen by the approaching column of soldiers."
    "Nos aseguramos de que no nos viera la columna de soldados que se acercaba."

# game/episode018.rpy:789
translate spanish ep018_temple_c9b7a648:

#   "The idea was to emerge around the back of the temple, pretending to be a patrol, and join the approaching soldiers near the entrance."
    "La idea era salir por la parte trasera del templo, fingiendo ser una patrulla, y unirse a los soldados que se acercaban cerca de la entrada."

# game/episode018.rpy:791
translate spanish ep018_temple_3fd8a2a4:

#   "We didn’t encounter any sentries, nor rival patrols, so we could merge neatly with the soldiers who had arrived by the time we came around the corner."
    "No encontramos centinelas ni patrullas rivales, así que pudimos mezclarnos sin problemas con los soldados que habían llegado cuando doblamos la esquina."

# game/episode018.rpy:792
translate spanish ep018_temple_6b518aa9:

#   "The main hall of the temple was crowding with soldiers, personnel and the machinery that had been brought in over the past few days."
    "La sala principal del templo estaba abarrotada de soldados, personal y la maquinaria que se había traído en los últimos días."

# game/episode018.rpy:794
translate spanish ep018_temple_e20e64ca:

#   "Agust, Kvi, the Confessor and Erylin were standing in front of the door that was deemed impenetrable when the Sovereignty forces had just arrived at the temple."
    "Agust, Kvi, la Confesora y Erylin se encontraban frente a la puerta considerada impenetrable cuando las fuerzas del Soberano acababan de llegar al templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:796
translate spanish ep018_temple_3f42c856:

#   "The workmen had visibly chiseled, carved, and battered away at the door."
    "Los obreros habían cincelado, tallado y golpeado visiblemente la puerta."

# game/episode018.rpy:797
translate spanish ep018_temple_b8556bdb:

#   "They must have succeeded in opening it, considering the foreman who was positively beaming in front of it."
    "Deben de haber conseguido abrirla, teniendo en cuenta que el capataz estaba radiante delante de ella."

# game/episode018.rpy:798
translate spanish ep018_temple_f7009905:

#   ag "Well, what are you waiting for, open it up?"
    ag "Bueno, ¿a qué esperas para abrirlo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:800
translate spanish ep018_temple_f68aa9fb:

#   "My father, ever a beacon of patience, managed to wipe the satisfied smile from the foreman’s face in a heartbeat."
    "Mi padre, siempre un faro de paciencia, consiguió borrar en un santiamén la sonrisa de satisfacción del capataz."

# game/episode018.rpy:801
translate spanish ep018_temple_c04eef80:

#   "The overseer ordered a couple of the workmen to push at the door, which began to inch open with a dusty groan."
    "El capataz ordenó a un par de obreros que empujaran la puerta, que empezó a abrirse con un gemido polvoriento."

# game/episode018.rpy:802
translate spanish ep018_temple_1dde0a46:

#   "Agust and company waited with thinly-veiled impatience for the reveal of the room behind the door."
    "Agust y compañía esperaron con impaciencia apenas disimulada a que se descubriera la habitación que había tras la puerta."

# game/episode018.rpy:804
translate spanish ep018_temple_c0cf855c:

#   "The chamber behind the door bathed in a purple glow."
    "La cámara tras la puerta se bañó en un resplandor púrpura."

# game/episode018.rpy:805
translate spanish ep018_temple_30d7609c:

#   "The workers stepped aside to allow Agust and the others a clear view."
    "Los trabajadores se hicieron a un lado para permitir que Agust y los demás tuvieran una visión clara."

# game/episode018.rpy:807
translate spanish ep018_temple_5c7314eb:

#   ag "So this is it?"
    ag "¿Así que esto es todo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:809
translate spanish ep018_temple_6fd367da:

#   co "Yes, this is the key."
    co "Sí, ésta es la clave."

# game/episode018.rpy:810
translate spanish ep018_temple_f3df1f86:

#   ag "Finally."
    ag "Por fin."

# game/episode018.rpy:812
translate spanish ep018_temple_859d2315:

#   ag "Load the thing on a transport, we’re done here."
    ag "Carga la cosa en un transporte, hemos terminado aquí."

# game/episode018.rpy:815
translate spanish ep018_temple_2851ec34:

#   man "Sir, shouldn’t we check for boobytraps, or if the object can be lifted at all?"
    man "Señor, ¿no deberíamos comprobar si hay trampas o si el objeto se puede levantar?"

# game/episode018.rpy:816
translate spanish ep018_temple_f3174631:

#   ag "Is this thing likely to be trapped, Confessor?"
    ag "¿Es probable que esta cosa quede atrapada, Confesora?"

# game/episode018.rpy:818
translate spanish ep018_temple_a78ef157:

#   co "Unlikely, but one can never be sure."
    co "Poco probable, pero nunca se puede estar seguro."

# game/episode018.rpy:820
translate spanish ep018_temple_6238ed72:

#   ag "See, no danger."
    ag "Ves, no hay peligro."

# game/episode018.rpy:821
translate spanish ep018_temple_0cd1a294:

#   ag "You have your orders, get that thing on a transport so we can get out of here."
    ag "Tienes tus órdenes, pon esa cosa en un transporte para que podamos salir de aquí."

# game/episode018.rpy:822
translate spanish ep018_temple_d4ed9e80:

#   ag "You’ve wasted enough time already."
    ag "Ya has perdido bastante tiempo."

# game/episode018.rpy:823
translate spanish ep018_temple_17ca49c6:

#   ag "We’re heading back, if that thing doesn’t come through the gate in one hour I’ll see you demoted."
    ag "Estamos volviendo, si esa cosa no pasa por la puerta en una hora te veré degradado."

# game/episode018.rpy:825
translate spanish ep018_temple_bc96ffa0:

#   man "Yes sir, it will be done, sir."
    man "Sí señor, se hará, señor."

# game/episode018.rpy:827
translate spanish ep018_temple_aee57b0e:

#   ki "Now what are we going to do?"
    ki "¿Y ahora qué vamos a hacer?"

# game/episode018.rpy:828
translate spanish ep018_temple_c7e0d57c:

#   c "We’re going to ride that transport and steal it once it reaches Taagmar."
    c "Vamos a montar en ese transporte y robarlo una vez que llegue a Taagmar."

# game/episode018.rpy:829
translate spanish ep018_temple_65938700:

#   ki "How?"
    ki "¿Cómo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:830
translate spanish ep018_temple_3c5ca4d3:

#   c "Just follow my lead."
    c "Sígueme la corriente."

# game/episode018.rpy:840
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_f33dbc1e:

#   c "What did you make of that little performance of the Confessor back at the Arch?"
    c "¿Qué te pareció esa pequeña representación de la Confesora en el Arco?"

# game/episode018.rpy:841
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_d1731160:

#   na "It was rather theatrical, but Agust and the rest of them seemed to take it seriously."
    na "Era bastante teatral, pero Agust y el resto parecían tomárselo en serio."

# game/episode018.rpy:842
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_09366684:

#   c "Yes, they did."
    c "Sí, lo hicieron."

# game/episode018.rpy:843
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_400b1eea:

#   c "He must have planned a lot of it beforehand."
    c "Debe haber planeado mucho de antemano."

# game/episode018.rpy:845
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_a378c4a8:

#   na "Yes, I think he knew where the Arch was and how to activate it."
    na "Sí, creo que sabía dónde estaba el Arco y cómo activarlo."

# game/episode018.rpy:846
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_ce4fc87d:

#   na "The hocus pocus wasn’t necessary, but it seemed effective."
    na "El abracadabra no era necesario, pero parecía eficaz."

# game/episode018.rpy:847
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_a25167bc:

#   c "Why do you think the Confessor is trying to fulfill the Prophecy?"
    c "¿Por qué crees que la Confesora intenta cumplir la Profecía?"

# game/episode018.rpy:848
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_83d8cefc:

#   na "The wording is very vague, unfortunately."
    na "Por desgracia, la redacción es muy vaga."

# game/episode018.rpy:849
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_37d8cdbc:

#   na "It’s likely the promise of power that draws him."
    na "Probablemente sea la promesa de poder lo que le atrae."

# game/episode018.rpy:850
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_2b506b64:

#   c "Power?"
    c "¿Poder?"

# game/episode018.rpy:852
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_d89976e0:

#   na "It just seems to be something a person like the Confessor is interested in."
    na "Parece ser algo que le interesa a una persona como la Confesora."

# game/episode018.rpy:853
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_a7444a26:

#   na "Agust sure is."
    na "Agust seguro que sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:855
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_df9c466d:

#   c "Quite a performance of the Confessor back at the Arch, don’t you think?"
    c "Vaya actuación de la Confesora en el Arco, ¿no crees?"

# game/episode018.rpy:856
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_44bda013:

#   na "Seems exactly the kind of thing Agust finds impressive."
    na "Parece exactamente el tipo de cosas que Agust encuentra impresionantes."

# game/episode018.rpy:857
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_8f1b7c19:

#   na "He did like those dreadful three-penny melodramas back when we were young."
    na "Le gustaban esos horribles melodramas de tres peniques cuando éramos jóvenes."

# game/episode018.rpy:858
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_efe03d33:

#   na "Some old guy waving his hands dramatically, pretending to be a wizard, has just the right melodramatic power Agust likes."
    na "Un viejo agitando las manos dramáticamente, fingiendo ser un mago, tiene justo el poder melodramático que le gusta a Agust."

# game/episode018.rpy:859
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_dce8b2e0:

#   c "What do you think the Key in the temple is?"
    c "¿Qué crees que es la Llave en el templo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:861
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_147f8ce3:

#   na "That’s a good question."
    na "Buena pregunta."

# game/episode018.rpy:862
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_18822e8f:

#   na "A key of course implies that there’s something that will unlock."
    na "Una llave implica, por supuesto, que hay algo que se abrirá."

# game/episode018.rpy:863
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_1db38fb2:

#   c "Another gateway perhaps?"
    c "¿Otro portal quizás?"

# game/episode018.rpy:864
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_641737c2:

#   na "A very likely possibility."
    na "Una posibilidad muy probable."

# game/episode018.rpy:865
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_761ca71a:

#   na "I keep wondering who built all this."
    na "Sigo preguntándome quién construyó todo esto."

# game/episode018.rpy:866
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_43d76748:

#   na "The architecture doesn’t feel very familiar, nor do the construction materials that were used."
    na "La arquitectura no me resulta muy familiar, ni tampoco los materiales de construcción utilizados."

# game/episode018.rpy:867
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_ee89e3e7:

#   c "I mostly see a lot of rubble."
    c "Veo sobre todo muchos escombros."

# game/episode018.rpy:869
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_7763a6ae:

#   na "There’s that, but the structures that are still standing, more or less, are very simple."
    na "Ahí está eso, pero las estructuras que siguen en pie, más o menos, son muy sencillas."

# game/episode018.rpy:870
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_675eb294:

#   na "These ruins might be very old, as is the temple."
    na "Estas ruinas podrían ser muy antiguas, al igual que el templo."

# game/episode018.rpy:871
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_b21f9a53:

#   c "This was once a sprawling metropolis, with the temple at its centre?"
    c "Esto fue una vez una metrópolis en expansión, con el templo en su centro..."

# game/episode018.rpy:872
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_07fdf6f2:

#   na "Possibly."
    na "Posiblemente."

# game/episode018.rpy:873
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_8a59bf08:

#   na "The temple is older though, so the city must have grown around it."
    na "Sin embargo, el templo es más antiguo, por lo que la ciudad debió de crecer a su alrededor."

# game/episode018.rpy:874
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_4a34ab3c:

#   c "And then it all fell to ruin at some point."
    c "Y luego todo se vino abajo en algún momento."

# game/episode018.rpy:875
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_b85d1c70:

#   na "Yes, though that has happened a long time ago as well."
    na "Sí, aunque eso también ocurrió hace mucho tiempo."

# game/episode018.rpy:876
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_625ff8d6:

#   c "No chance of meeting the locals then?"
    c "¿No hay posibilidad de conocer a los lugareños?"

# game/episode018.rpy:878
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_1050c096:

#   na "There’s always a chance, but it’s a very slim one."
    na "Siempre hay una posibilidad, pero muy pequeña."

# game/episode018.rpy:879
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_cff0dca4:

#   c "Maybe they’ve migrated to another part of the planet, or whatever this place is."
    c "Tal vez han emigrado a otra parte del planeta, o lo que sea este lugar."

# game/episode018.rpy:881
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_79043e8b:

#   na "In that case we still lack the means to travel large distances."
    na "En ese caso, seguimos careciendo de medios para recorrer grandes distancias."

# game/episode018.rpy:882
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_7fcbea74:

#   c "Let’s stick close to our mortal enemies in that case."
    c "Mantengámonos cerca de nuestros enemigos mortales en ese caso."

# game/episode018.rpy:884
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_7ede79d3:

#   na "Quite."
    na "Bastante."

# game/episode018.rpy:886
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_6010ab43:

#   na "How are you holding up?"
    na "¿Cómo lo llevas?"

# game/episode018.rpy:887
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_4d3f3918:

#   c "In what way?"
    c "¿En qué sentido?"

# game/episode018.rpy:889
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_6900c492:

#   na "Well, I can’t imagine the trek across the desert was a relaxing experience."
    na "Bueno, no puedo imaginar que la travesía del desierto fuera una experiencia relajante."

# game/episode018.rpy:890
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_33e396db:

#   na "Eva mentioned you were out of water when the mercenaries found you."
    na "Eva mencionó que estabas sin agua cuando los mercenarios te encontraron."

# game/episode018.rpy:891
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_8637cbb7:

#   c "Just about, yeah."
    c "Casi, sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:892
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_03371d26:

#   c "It’s been such a rush from the moment we left Altum Station and crashed into that desert."
    c "Ha sido un subidón desde el momento en que salimos de la estación de Altum y nos estrellamos contra ese desierto."

# game/episode018.rpy:893
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_e7528bb7:

#   c "The nights were terrible."
    c "Las noches eran terribles."

# game/episode018.rpy:894
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_e7d33841:

#   na "Cold?"
    na "¿Frío?"

# game/episode018.rpy:895
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_a54a9bb3:

#   c "That, but the dreams didn’t help."
    c "Eso, pero los sueños no ayudaron."

# game/episode018.rpy:897
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_96aee6f9:

#   na "What did you dream about?"
    na "¿Con qué has soñado?"

# game/episode018.rpy:898
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_970202f0:

#   c "The Scolguin Queen and her court came for a visit."
    c "La reina Scolguin y su corte vinieron de visita."

# game/episode018.rpy:900
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_600039e8:

#   na "Maybe your subconscious processing past events?"
    na "¿Quizás tu subconsciente procesando eventos pasados?"

# game/episode018.rpy:901
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_fe99f19a:

#   c "Maybe...{w} It felt too real though."
    c "Tal vez ... {w} Se sentía demasiado real sin embargo."

# game/episode018.rpy:902
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_47ad1421:

#   c "Like they have their hooks inside my mind now, after the Tasting, I mean."
    c "Como si tuvieran sus ganchos dentro de mi mente ahora, después de la Cata, quiero decir."

# game/episode018.rpy:904
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_ba296797:

#   na "It sounds that they have managed something like that."
    na "Parece que han conseguido algo así."

# game/episode018.rpy:905
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_476431b6:

#   c "Yeah. Not great."
    c "Sí. No muy bien."

# game/episode018.rpy:907
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_e420a9be:

#   c "That’s why I won’t let them touch you anytime ever."
    c "Por eso no dejaré que te toquen nunca."

# game/episode018.rpy:909
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_097a3725:

#   na "We’ve made a deal with them, [p_name_short]."
    na "Hemos hecho un trato con ellos, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode018.rpy:910
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_25b903e2:

#   c "Deals can be renegotiated."
    c "Los acuerdos pueden renegociarse."

# game/episode018.rpy:912
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_01733627:

#   c "That’s why I’m not going to let them touch me anytime ever."
    c "Por eso no voy a dejar que me toquen nunca."

# game/episode018.rpy:913
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_4fc26193:

#   na "Good idea, but how will you manage that?"
    na "Buena idea, pero ¿cómo lo va a conseguir?"

# game/episode018.rpy:915
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_4acc2f14:

#   na "It’s us against an entire species."
    na "Somos nosotros contra toda una especie."

# game/episode018.rpy:916
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_468d7316:

#   c "We’ll find a way."
    c "Encontraremos la manera."

# game/episode018.rpy:917
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_794c1b4c:

#   c "Besides, we still have ten years to find a solution."
    c "Además, aún tenemos diez años para encontrar una solución."

# game/episode018.rpy:919
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_78ed2c50:

#   na "I hope that’s enough time."
    na "Espero que sea tiempo suficiente."

# game/episode018.rpy:922
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_c7bdde9c:

#   "I embraced my mother in response and we stood together for a while, overlooking the ancient plain."
    "Abracé a mi madre en respuesta y permanecimos juntas durante un rato, contemplando la antigua llanura."

# game/episode018.rpy:924
translate spanish ep018_ruins_nadya_35711bd8:

#   "I embraced Nadya in response and we stood together for a while, overlooking the ancient plain."
    "Abracé a Nadya en respuesta y permanecimos juntos un rato, con vistas a la antigua llanura."

# game/episode018.rpy:933
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_164c0894:

#   c "Are you doing okay?"
    c "¿Estás bien?"

# game/episode018.rpy:935
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_98cf3653:

#   ve "Sure."
    ve "Sí, claro."

# game/episode018.rpy:937
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_d98e55a2:

#   ve "Though it’s strange to see the Confessor after all this time, even from a distance."
    ve "Aunque es extraño ver a la Confesora después de tanto tiempo, aunque sea de lejos."

# game/episode018.rpy:938
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_0da57f1a:

#   c "I can imagine."
    c "Me lo imagino."

# game/episode018.rpy:939
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_d2240100:

#   c "You knew him quite well, didn’t you?"
    c "Le conocías bastante bien, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode018.rpy:941
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_67a658b4:

#   c "I want to talk to you about the Confessor."
    c "Quiero hablarte de la Confesora."

# game/episode018.rpy:943
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_187aa480:

#   ve "Of course."
    ve "Por supuesto."

# game/episode018.rpy:944
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_c18a529c:

#   c "You knew him quite well, right?"
    c "Le conocías bastante bien, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode018.rpy:946
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_5f9b602b:

#   ve "He was like a father to me, or a grandfather, to be more accurate."
    ve "Era como un padre para mí, o un abuelo, para ser más exactos."

# game/episode018.rpy:947
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_31e2118a:

#   c "You said he’s fond of impressing people with his alleged magical abilities."
    c "Dijiste que le gusta impresionar a la gente con sus supuestas habilidades mágicas."

# game/episode018.rpy:948
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_334da882:

#   ve "Yes, it’s part of his persona."
    ve "Sí, es parte de su personalidad."

# game/episode018.rpy:949
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_ac3f358b:

#   ve "His Handmaidens are aware of the truth, of course and he confided in me a lot."
    ve "Sus Siervas son conscientes de la verdad, por supuesto, y él confió mucho en mí."

# game/episode018.rpy:950
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_758afe1f:

#   ve "The way he works is that he always tries to be the person in the room who knows the most about everything and also knows all there is about everyone else in the room."
    ve "Siempre intenta ser la persona de la sala que más sabe de todo y que también sabe todo lo que hay sobre los demás."

# game/episode018.rpy:951
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_9335f330:

#   ve "Before he swoops in to convert or recruit potential allies, his Handmaidens will have covertly gathered information months before."
    ve "Antes de lanzarse en picado a convertir o reclutar aliados potenciales, sus Siervas habrán recabado información de forma encubierta meses antes."

# game/episode018.rpy:952
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_d9860706:

#   ve "Anything that will give him an edge over someone else."
    ve "Cualquier cosa que le dé ventaja sobre los demás."

# game/episode018.rpy:953
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_1caace9e:

#   ve "When the operation actually kicks off and the Confessor visits a point or person of interest, the encounter will have been planned out from the start."
    ve "Cuando la operación se pone en marcha y la Confesora visita un punto o una persona de interés, el encuentro se habrá planificado desde el principio."

# game/episode018.rpy:954
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_96aad39c:

#   c "So, that performance before the Arch?"
    c "Entonces, ¿esa actuación ante el Arco?"

# game/episode018.rpy:956
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_ad277a74:

#   ve "That surely wasn’t improvised in the spur of the moment."
    ve "Eso seguro que no se improvisó de improviso."

# game/episode018.rpy:958
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_a48e9963:

#   ve "The Confessor must have known about the Arch and the procedure to activate it."
    ve "La Confesora debía conocer el Arco y el procedimiento para activarlo."

# game/episode018.rpy:959
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_875e3410:

#   ve "The gestures and practical effects were also prepared in advance."
    ve "Los gestos y efectos prácticos también se prepararon con antelación."

# game/episode018.rpy:960
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_fc589f57:

#   c "And people buy those tricks?"
    c "¿Y la gente compra esos trucos?"

# game/episode018.rpy:962
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_69d28b08:

#   ve "Mostly, yes."
    ve "En general, sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:963
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_3afb223d:

#   ve "The Confessor is a very confident man, charismatic as well."
    ve "El Confesor es un hombre muy seguro de sí mismo, también carismático."

# game/episode018.rpy:964
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_f10740ec:

#   ve "And he’s driven as well, his whole life is dedicated to pursuing the Prophecy."
    ve "Y también está motivado, toda su vida está dedicada a perseguir la Profecía."

# game/episode018.rpy:965
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_05a91b11:

#   c "What does he hope to gain by it?"
    c "¿Qué espera ganar con ello?"

# game/episode018.rpy:966
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_85392205:

#   ve "Power, or the promise of it."
    ve "Poder, o la promesa de poder."

# game/episode018.rpy:967
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_36cbad3f:

#   c "That still sounds a little vague."
    c "Eso sigue sonando un poco vago."

# game/episode018.rpy:969
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_eebd9945:

#   ve "It is, but the promise of wielding it is good enough for the Confessor."
    ve "Lo es, pero la promesa de blandirla es suficiente para la Confesora."

# game/episode018.rpy:970
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_d9a48a7c:

#   c "Probably the reason my father is interested all of a sudden as well."
    c "Probablemente también sea la razón por la que mi padre se ha interesado de repente."

# game/episode018.rpy:971
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_2ff07529:

#   ve "From what I know of your father, that seems likely."
    ve "Por lo que sé de tu padre, eso parece probable."

# game/episode018.rpy:972
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_7cf974d2:

#   c "Did the Confessor share a lot of his secrets with you?"
    c "¿Compartió la Confesora muchos de sus secretos con usted?"

# game/episode018.rpy:974
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_55efba57:

#   ve "I was supposed to be his surrogate grandchild, remember?"
    ve "Se suponía que yo era su nieto sustituto, ¿recuerdas?"

# game/episode018.rpy:975
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_d8d5bdf2:

#   ve "So he told me about the sleights of hand he liked to perform in order to impress gullible would-be believers."
    ve "Así que me habló de los juegos de manos que le gustaba hacer para impresionar a los crédulos creyentes."

# game/episode018.rpy:977
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_f762ce8f:

#   ve "But his interpretation of the Prophecy or his goals he kept hidden even from me."
    ve "Pero su interpretación de la Profecía o sus objetivos los mantuvo ocultos incluso para mí."

# game/episode018.rpy:979
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_83e3bdd5:

#   ve "Looking back at it all, almost everything he told me was a means of instructing me."
    ve "Mirándolo todo en retrospectiva, casi todo lo que me decía era para instruirme."

# game/episode018.rpy:980
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_12e45821:

#   c "What do you mean exactly?"
    c "¿Qué quiere decir exactamente?"

# game/episode018.rpy:981
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_83a76cca:

#   ve "He tried to mold me from a young age."
    ve "Intentó moldearme desde muy joven."

# game/episode018.rpy:982
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_9f9feba5:

#   ve "Slipping in enough personal details, but all the time adjusting my view on life a certain way."
    ve "Introduciendo suficientes detalles personales, pero todo el tiempo ajustando mi visión de la vida de una determinada manera."

# game/episode018.rpy:983
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_fd8f378e:

#   ve "What do you do when you enter a room full of people?"
    ve "¿Qué haces cuando entras en una habitación llena de gente?"

# game/episode018.rpy:984
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_297d93f3:

#   c "What?"
    c "¿Cómo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:985
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_049e0f8c:

#   c "Uh...{w} I don’t know, see if it’s someone I know and strike up a conversation?"
    c "Uh...{w} No sé, ¿ver si es alguien que conozco y entablar una conversación?"

# game/episode018.rpy:987
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_fa0b6d63:

#   ve "It’s different for me."
    ve "Para mí es diferente."

# game/episode018.rpy:988
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_d5eb8791:

#   ve "When I enter a room, I first mark all the possible exits."
    ve "Cuando entro en una habitación, primero marco todas las salidas posibles."

# game/episode018.rpy:990
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_d9a6ae49:

#   ve "Right after that, I mark all potential threats and confirm which people are unlikely to cause trouble."
    ve "Inmediatamente después, marco todas las amenazas potenciales y confirmo qué personas tienen pocas probabilidades de causar problemas."

# game/episode018.rpy:991
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_a373f32d:

#   ve "There’s a list of other things that were drilled into me like that, but striking up a conversation is one of the last items on that list."
    ve "Hay una lista de otras cosas que me inculcaron así, pero entablar una conversación es uno de los últimos puntos de esa lista."

# game/episode018.rpy:992
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_f5f7c27d:

#   c "Right."
    c "Bien."

# game/episode018.rpy:993
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_045cbdf0:

#   c "You’re saying the Confessor is the same?"
    c "¿Estás diciendo que la Confesora es la misma?"

# game/episode018.rpy:994
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_9f781acd:

#   ve "He always comes prepared."
    ve "Siempre viene preparado."

# game/episode018.rpy:995
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_82def46b:

#   ve "If he isn’t prepared, he’ll improvise, but I know for a fact he hates that."
    ve "Si no está preparado, improvisará, pero sé a ciencia cierta que odia eso."

# game/episode018.rpy:996
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_c5aed8d5:

#   c "Interesting."
    c "Interesante."

# game/episode018.rpy:997
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_d8ed24c8:

#   c "I’ll guess we’ll have to surprise him if we ever take him on."
    c "Supongo que tendremos que sorprenderle si alguna vez le contratamos."

# game/episode018.rpy:999
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_2b0ce451:

#   ve "I guess so."
    ve "Supongo que sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:1001
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_bca6af8e:

#   "We were both silent for a while, Vess staring out across the plain."
    "Ambos permanecimos en silencio durante un rato, Vess con la mirada perdida en la llanura."

# game/episode018.rpy:1003
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_2f22199b:

#   ve "I keep wondering if his story about my mother being alive was just a ploy to keep me loyal."
    ve "Sigo preguntándome si su historia de que mi madre estaba viva era sólo una estratagema para fidelizarme."

# game/episode018.rpy:1004
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_3f9be425:

#   c "Judging from what you’ve just told me, that sounds like a thing he’d be capable of."
    c "A juzgar por lo que acabas de contarme, eso parece algo de lo que sería capaz."

# game/episode018.rpy:1006
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_0c5eea44:

#   ve "Yes, that’s true."
    ve "Sí, es cierto."

# game/episode018.rpy:1008
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_434183e9:

#   ve "But the photograph he showed me, it looked so real."
    ve "Pero la fotografía que me enseñó, parecía tan real."

# game/episode018.rpy:1009
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_99ff405f:

#   ve "Then again, any photo can be doctored."
    ve "Por otra parte, cualquier foto puede ser manipulada."

# game/episode018.rpy:1010
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_1a40c360:

#   ve "Or maybe it was just a picture of a woman who looked somewhat like me."
    ve "O tal vez sólo era la foto de una mujer que se parecía a mí."

# game/episode018.rpy:1011
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_570e2565:

#   c "I think it’s rather cruel to spring this on you, without ever providing any further context."
    c "Me parece un poco cruel soltarte esto sin darte más contexto."

# game/episode018.rpy:1013
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_cbfc5d90:

#   ve "It got him my cooperation to betray you one final time."
    ve "Consiguió mi cooperación para traicionarte una última vez."

# game/episode018.rpy:1014
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_bf09e84e:

#   c "I guess that made it all worth it."
    c "Supongo que eso hizo que mereciera la pena."

# game/episode018.rpy:1017
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_058d9b44:

#   c "I have a feeling we’re going to be dealing with the Confessor a lot in the near future."
    c "Tengo la sensación de que vamos a tratar mucho con la Confesora en un futuro próximo."

# game/episode018.rpy:1019
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_7ea32ae9:

#   c "If we ever get the chance to find out more about your mother, we’ll take it."
    c "Si alguna vez tenemos la oportunidad de saber más sobre tu madre, la aprovecharemos."

# game/episode018.rpy:1021
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_f007dfd7:

#   ve "Really, you’d do that for me?"
    ve "¿En serio, harías eso por mí?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1022
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_f67fe448:

#   c "Of course, you deserve the truth and at least some closure."
    c "Por supuesto, te mereces la verdad y al menos un cierre."

# game/episode018.rpy:1024
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_df42574f:

#   ve "Thank you, [p_name_short]."
    ve "Gracias, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode018.rpy:1026
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_8755f436:

#   "Tears rimmed her eyes as she stared out over the plain again."
    "Se le llenaron los ojos de lágrimas al contemplar de nuevo la llanura."

# game/episode018.rpy:1028
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_34161163:

#   "My hand slipped in hers and together we watched the sun go down behind the temple across the plains."
    "Mi mano se deslizó entre las suyas y juntos contemplamos la puesta de sol tras el templo, al otro lado de la llanura."

# game/episode018.rpy:1030
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_a201417b:

#   ve "I think so too."
    ve "Yo también lo creo."

# game/episode018.rpy:1031
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_461ad443:

#   c "We’d better be prepared."
    c "Será mejor que estemos preparados."

# game/episode018.rpy:1033
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_3b1d33d2:

#   ve "I’ll help in every way I can."
    ve "Ayudaré en todo lo que pueda."

# game/episode018.rpy:1034
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_4e8c7062:

#   c "Of course."
    c "Por supuesto."

# game/episode018.rpy:1035
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_c562c5f0:

#   c "Don’t stay out here in the open too long, you might get spotted."
    c "No te quedes mucho tiempo a la intemperie, podrían descubrirte."

# game/episode018.rpy:1038
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_5e2b29b5:

#   ve "Yes, master."
    ve "Sí, amo."

# game/episode018.rpy:1040
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_77cb9752:

#   ve "I'll be careful."
    ve "Tendré cuidado."

# game/episode018.rpy:1016
translate spanish ep018_ruins_vess_2b0ce451_1:

#   ve "I guess so."
    ve "Supongo que sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:1048
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_3c8e0458:

#   "The night was very quiet, but I couldn’t sleep."
    "La noche fue muy tranquila, pero no pude dormir."

# game/episode018.rpy:1049
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_d80fea11:

#   "I got out of my sleeping bag and went out into the square."
    "Me levanté del saco de dormir y salí a la plaza."

# game/episode018.rpy:1050
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_e543bf27:

#   "Kit was standing guard, but I didn’t feel like striking up a conversation with him."
    "Kit estaba de guardia, pero no me apetecía entablar conversación con él."

# game/episode018.rpy:1051
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_f3f56992:

#   "Instead, I wandered around the ruins."
    "En lugar de eso, deambulé por las ruinas."

# game/episode018.rpy:1053
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_673973c3:

#   "As I was about to return to the building I’d put down my sleeping bag, Aven stepped out from behind a pillar."
    "Cuando estaba a punto de volver al edificio donde había dejado el saco de dormir, Aven salió de detrás de un pilar."

# game/episode018.rpy:1055
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_110474fc:

#   av "Oh!"
    av "¡Oh!"

# game/episode018.rpy:1056
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_1052d2e7:

#   c "Couldn’t sleep either?"
    c "¿Tampoco podías dormir?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1057
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_76024095:

#   av "No, it could be this place or the events of the past few days."
    av "No, podría ser este lugar o los acontecimientos de los últimos días."

# game/episode018.rpy:1058
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_a040a00c:

#   c "It’s a lot to take in, I reckon?"
    c "Creo que es mucho para asimilar."

# game/episode018.rpy:1059
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_77274c31:

#   av "Yes."
    av "Sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:1060
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_d4be95a4:

#   "We both sat down against a crumbling wall."
    "Ambos nos sentamos contra una pared derruida."

# game/episode018.rpy:1062
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_753424f3:

#   av "Me and mom lived relatively insulated from the Sovereignty back on Ryūjin Prime."
    av "Mamá y yo vivíamos relativamente aislados de la Soberanía en Ryūjin Prime."

# game/episode018.rpy:1063
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_fe9af784:

#   av "Of course we heard about what the Sovereignty was capable of, but..."
    av "Claro que nos enteramos de lo que era capaz el Soberano, pero..."

# game/episode018.rpy:1064
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_2c9f4fcf:

#   c "Seeing it happen is different from hearing about it?"
    c "¿Verlo no es lo mismo que oír hablar de ello?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1066
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_7e2f38ea:

#   av "Exactly."
    av "Exactamente."

# game/episode018.rpy:1067
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_b0d6f41e:

#   av "They stop at nothing, do they?"
    av "No se detienen ante nada, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1068
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_0a10c0ee:

#   c "No, they don’t."
    c "No, no lo hacen."

# game/episode018.rpy:1069
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_013fd726:

#   c "Especially with dad at the helm..."
    c "Especialmente con papá al timón..."

# game/episode018.rpy:1071
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_ede09921:

#   av "God, it sounds so awkward, you saying that."
    av "Dios, suena tan incómodo que digas eso."

# game/episode018.rpy:1072
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_297d93f3:

#   c "What?"
    c "¿Cómo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1074
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_b85a14d4:

#   av "“Dad”, like he’s my father too."
    av "\"Papá\", como si también fuera mi padre."

# game/episode018.rpy:1075
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_d7b03860:

#   av "And of course he apparently is, but it still just doesn’t feel like he is."
    av "Y por supuesto que aparentemente lo es, pero aún así no parece que lo sea."

# game/episode018.rpy:1076
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_eba67bfe:

#   av "Do you know what I mean?"
    av "¿Sabes a qué me refiero?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1077
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_3275e9ef:

#   c "I think so."
    c "Creo que sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:1078
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_cb437275:

#   c "It still feels a little unreal sometimes."
    c "A veces sigue pareciendo un poco irreal."

# game/episode018.rpy:1079
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_f6fab4bf:

#   c "Especially considering the way we’re involved with each other."
    c "Sobre todo teniendo en cuenta la forma en que nos relacionamos."

# game/episode018.rpy:1081
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_f0444eee:

#   av "What a romantic way to describe our relationship!"
    av "¡Qué manera tan romántica de describir nuestra relación!"

# game/episode018.rpy:1082
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_230c6093:

#   c "I know, I’m ever the hopeless romantic."
    c "Lo sé, soy una romántica empedernida."

# game/episode018.rpy:1084
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_7cdfa386:

#   av "Agust was always a very distant presence, a long forgotten boogeyman at times, but now that I know he fathered me and treated mom so badly, I just hate him."
    av "Agust siempre fue una presencia muy distante, un hombre del saco olvidado a veces, pero ahora que sé que me engendró y que trató tan mal a mamá, simplemente le odio."

# game/episode018.rpy:1085
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_1d5ed376:

#   c "Not trying to one-up you, but I hated him with a passion long before that."
    c "No es por superarte, pero le odiaba con pasión mucho antes de eso."

# game/episode018.rpy:1087
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_8f90ff9a:

#   av "Haha, you win."
    av "Jaja, tú ganas."

# game/episode018.rpy:1088
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_1b7834ca:

#   c "Agust’s presence is best savored at a long distance, preferably lightyears away."
    c "La presencia de Agust se saborea mejor a larga distancia, preferiblemente a años luz."

# game/episode018.rpy:1090
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_7c2ae5bd:

#   av "What do you think he hopes to gain in that temple?"
    av "¿Qué crees que espera ganar en ese templo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1091
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_28ad9ff2:

#   c "I’m not sure, but I’m certain it’s something that he will want to benefit from, at the cost of thousands of others."
    c "No estoy seguro, pero estoy seguro de que es algo de lo que él querrá beneficiarse, a costa de otros miles de personas."

# game/episode018.rpy:1093
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_0310355f:

#   av "I think that’s a low estimation."
    av "Creo que es una estimación baja."

# game/episode018.rpy:1094
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_5c21ce98:

#   c "Yeah, the Taagmar didn’t stand a chance."
    c "Sí, el Taagmar no tenía ninguna posibilidad."

# game/episode018.rpy:1096
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_31b88be7:

#   av "Ugh, I didn’t want to steer the conversation into such gloomy territory."
    av "No quería llevar la conversación a un terreno tan sombrío."

# game/episode018.rpy:1097
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_58190467:

#   c "No harm done, we’ve lived through some gloomy stuff lately."
    c "No pasa nada, hemos vivido cosas sombrías últimamente."

# game/episode018.rpy:1098
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_06c84c72:

#   c "It just makes me want to appreciate the happy things all the more."
    c "Sólo hace que quiera apreciar aún más las cosas felices."

# game/episode018.rpy:1101
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_9667c979:

#   av "Such as?"
    av "¿Por ejemplo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1102
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_a721bb91:

#   c "Well, you, for instance."
    c "Bueno, tú, por ejemplo."

# game/episode018.rpy:1104
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_b071eecd:

#   av "I knew you were going to say that!"
    av "¡Sabía que ibas a decir eso!"

# game/episode018.rpy:1105
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_2b5ab5c4:

#   av "Not that I don’t want to hear you saying it, of course."
    av "No es que no quiera oírte decirlo, por supuesto."

# game/episode018.rpy:1106
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_b5f7a781:

#   c "I was starting to get a little worried there for a second."
    c "Empecé a preocuparme un poco por un segundo."

# game/episode018.rpy:1108
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_8dd467ad:

#   av "We don’t want that now, do we?"
    av "No queremos eso ahora, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1109
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_6fb17edf:

#   av "I have a thing or two in mind to make you happy..."
    av "Tengo un par de cosas en mente para hacerte feliz..."

# game/episode018.rpy:1110
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_1c431111:

#   c "Go on..."
    c "Sigue..."

# game/episode018.rpy:1112
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_a6b724b5:

#   av "I really think we should find a quiet place."
    av "Realmente creo que deberíamos encontrar un lugar tranquilo."

# game/episode018.rpy:1113
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_bfd3dbc1:

#   c "Kit is patrolling, but he should be on the other side of the perimeter now."
    c "Kit está patrullando, pero ahora debería estar al otro lado del perímetro."

# game/episode018.rpy:1114
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_78bc85da:

#   "Aven and I hurried to a corner of the ruins, well out of the way of where we were camped."
    "Aven y yo nos apresuramos hacia un rincón de las ruinas, bien lejos de donde estábamos acampados."

# game/episode018.rpy:1118
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_677f1c37:

#   "Aven shifted one of the straps of her shirt off her shoulder, revealing more of her flesh."
    "Aven se quitó uno de los tirantes de la camisa del hombro, mostrando más carne."

# game/episode018.rpy:1120
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_240d3f09:

#   "At that moment, several people rounded the corner of the building we were sitting against."
    "En ese momento, varias personas doblaron la esquina del edificio contra el que estábamos sentados."

# game/episode018.rpy:1121
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_66702b6c:

#   "Kit, Nadya and Thim were discussing something, but stopped when they saw us."
    "Kit, Nadya y Thim estaban discutiendo algo, pero se detuvieron al vernos."

# game/episode018.rpy:1123
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_9d672fa5:

#   ki "Enjoying the night sky?"
    ki "¿Disfruta del cielo nocturno?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1125
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_df91fa59:

#   av "We are."
    av "Lo somos."

# game/episode018.rpy:1127
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_fc53cfd4:

#   na "Could we borrow you for a moment?"
    na "¿Nos prestas un momento?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1128
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_05cee737:

#   av "I...{w} Uh...{w} Of course."
    av "Yo...{w} Uh...{w} Por supuesto."

# game/episode018.rpy:1130
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_dad40529:

#   "Aven stood up to join the others, regret in her eyes as she looked at me."
    "Aven se levantó para reunirse con los demás, con pesar en los ojos cuando me miró."

# game/episode018.rpy:1131
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_55a863bf:

#   av "Speak to you later?"
    av "¿Hablamos más tarde?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1132
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_4e8c7062:

#   c "Of course."
    c "Por supuesto."

# game/episode018.rpy:1134
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_30cda580:

#   "Oblivious to whatever they’d interrupted, Nadya and the others walked away with Aven."
    "Ajenos a lo que hubieran interrumpido, Nadya y los demás se alejaron con Aven."

# game/episode018.rpy:1135
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_0f092ba5:

#   "I remained behind, silently cursing them for the interruption."
    "Me quedé atrás, maldiciéndoles en silencio por la interrupción."

# game/episode018.rpy:1137
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_032da8d5:

#   av "Yes, I get that, I really do."
    av "Sí, lo entiendo, de verdad."

# game/episode018.rpy:1138
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_959a4a64:

#   av "I’m going to try and get some sleep if that’s alright with you."
    av "Voy a intentar dormir un poco, si te parece bien."

# game/episode018.rpy:1139
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_6221499d:

#   c "Of course, I think I’ll wander for just a little longer."
    c "Por supuesto, creo que vagaré un poco más."

# game/episode018.rpy:1141
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_61ed1684:

#   av "Don’t wander inside that temple by mistake, things might get unpleasant."
    av "No entres en ese templo por error, las cosas podrían ponerse desagradables."

# game/episode018.rpy:1142
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_3cf13b30:

#   c "I’ll try no to."
    c "Intentaré no hacerlo."

# game/episode018.rpy:1143
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_0850efde:

#   c "Good night, Aven."
    c "Buenas noches, Aven."

# game/episode018.rpy:1144
translate spanish ep018_ruins_aven_9d2022fd:

#   av "You too, [p_name_short]."
    av "Tú también, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode018.rpy:1152
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_fded0606:

#   "Raene was sitting alone in one of the small buildings, reading something on her tablet."
    "Raene estaba sentada sola en uno de los pequeños edificios, leyendo algo en su tableta."

# game/episode018.rpy:1153
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_f51625d1:

#   c "How do you like the accommodations?"
    c "¿Qué le parece el alojamiento?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1155
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_5af6fd11:

#   ra "They’re a little dusty, but otherwise fine."
    ra "Tienen un poco de polvo, pero por lo demás están bien."

# game/episode018.rpy:1156
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_c1d6c853:

#   ra "The heat in this place is terrible though."
    ra "Sin embargo, el calor en este lugar es terrible."

# game/episode018.rpy:1157
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_a048d163:

#   c "Yeah, it doesn’t really get any less warm during the day."
    c "Sí, realmente no hace menos calor durante el día."

# game/episode018.rpy:1158
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_c14a9163:

#   ra "The armored suit doesn’t help as well."
    ra "El traje blindado tampoco ayuda."

# game/episode018.rpy:1159
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_677e8f87:

#   c "No, the Sovereignty doesn’t make those for any kind of comfort."
    c "No, la Soberanía no las hace para ninguna comodidad."

# game/episode018.rpy:1160
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_4310e779:

#   c "I even doubt they provide as much protection either."
    c "Incluso dudo que proporcionen tanta protección."

# game/episode018.rpy:1161
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_4a5ce4af:

#   c "What are you reading?"
    c "¿Qué estás leyendo?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1163
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_71995779:

#   ra "Just some news articles I downloaded back on Altum Station."
    ra "Sólo algunos artículos de noticias que descargué en la estación Altum."

# game/episode018.rpy:1164
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_cf9904ff:

#   c "Anything in particular?"
    c "¿Algo en particular?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1166
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_e7d94834:

#   ra "You’re going to disapprove, but yeah, some things about my father."
    ra "Vas a desaprobarlo, pero sí, algunas cosas sobre mi padre."

# game/episode018.rpy:1167
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_f5f7c27d:

#   c "Right."
    c "Bien."

# game/episode018.rpy:1168
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_fdf60d32:

#   c "I don’t necessarily disapprove, but just be careful not to upset yourself."
    c "No lo desapruebo necesariamente, pero ten cuidado de no alterarte."

# game/episode018.rpy:1169
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_bd94ce1a:

#   c "From what I heard about Sacleus, he’s not the man to care about the feelings of others."
    c "Por lo que he oído de Sacleus, no es un hombre que se preocupe por los sentimientos de los demás."

# game/episode018.rpy:1171
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_1935c69c:

#   ra "He sure hasn’t changed his views, that’s for certain."
    ra "Seguro que no ha cambiado de opinión, eso es seguro."

# game/episode018.rpy:1172
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_2b5c0599:

#   ra "They’re still on the lookout for you and me."
    ra "Siguen buscándonos a ti y a mí."

# game/episode018.rpy:1174
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_0723fd52:

#   ra "Other than that it’s the same old rhetoric, the same old hang-ups."
    ra "Aparte de eso, es la misma retórica de siempre, los mismos complejos de siempre."

# game/episode018.rpy:1176
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_3a9891aa:

#   ra "And I find that it doesn’t bother me that much anymore."
    ra "Y me parece que ya no me molesta tanto."

# game/episode018.rpy:1178
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_092cefb0:

#   ra "Maybe now that he’s at a distance...{w} I don’t know."
    ra "Tal vez ahora que está a una distancia ... {w} No lo sé."

# game/episode018.rpy:1179
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_118385c1:

#   c "Not living in that kind of environment certainly helps."
    c "No vivir en ese tipo de entorno sin duda ayuda."

# game/episode018.rpy:1181
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_ea4ec5af:

#   ra "His words used to frighten me so much."
    ra "Sus palabras solían asustarme mucho."

# game/episode018.rpy:1182
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_79c50495:

#   ra "I really thought my actions, or even being who I am, had damned me forever."
    ra "Realmente pensé que mis acciones, o incluso ser quien soy, me habían condenado para siempre."

# game/episode018.rpy:1184
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_c91ed8d3:

#   ra "But hearing him now, droning on about sinful behavior, it sounds so hollow all of a sudden."
    ra "Pero escucharlo ahora, hablando de comportamiento pecaminoso, suena tan vacío de repente."

# game/episode018.rpy:1186
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_fd854585:

#   ra "And the way he speaks about me in his rants to keep his followers to hunt us just makes me furious."
    ra "Y la forma en que habla de mí en sus desplantes para mantener a sus seguidores a la caza de nosotros sólo me hace furioso."

# game/episode018.rpy:1187
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_b8e6381d:

#   ra "I mean, how dare he?!"
    ra "Quiero decir, ¡¿cómo se atreve?!"

# game/episode018.rpy:1188
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_62ef7433:

#   c "Your father is clearly someone whose opinions are rarely challenged."
    c "Está claro que tu padre es alguien cuyas opiniones rara vez se cuestionan."

# game/episode018.rpy:1189
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_2391d358:

#   c "He also has the blessed tenets of a supposed higher being on his side, neatly confirming his world views, not the best combination all considered."
    c "También tiene de su lado los benditos principios de un supuesto ser superior, que confirman claramente sus visiones del mundo, lo que no es la mejor combinación, todo sea dicho."

# game/episode018.rpy:1191
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_d860a4a7:

#   ra "I suppose not."
    ra "Supongo que no."

# game/episode018.rpy:1193
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_ad7ca662:

#   ra "I'm just so glad I met you on Verdigris."
    ra "Estoy tan contenta de haberte conocido en Verdigris."

# game/episode018.rpy:1194
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_e4c9d27e:

#   ra "Who knows where I would have ended up."
    ra "Quién sabe dónde habría acabado."

# game/episode018.rpy:1196
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_51de9475:

#   ra "Probably back into the arms of my father..."
    ra "Probablemente de vuelta a los brazos de mi padre..."

# game/episode018.rpy:1197
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_4b214a60:

#   c "I'm not so sure about that."
    c "No estoy tan seguro de eso."

# game/episode018.rpy:1198
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_b5f6f016:

#   c "You contacted Ziv's people way before the Bastard showed up."
    c "Contactaste con la gente de Ziv mucho antes de que el Bastardo apareciera."

# game/episode018.rpy:1200
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_a5e5ecea:

#   ra "That's true."
    ra "Eso es verdad."

# game/episode018.rpy:1201
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_61d83d38:

#   c "So, don't diminish yourself."
    c "Así que no te rebajes."

# game/episode018.rpy:1202
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_b776425c:

#   c "Deep down, you knew what you wanted and acted on it."
    c "En el fondo, sabías lo que querías y actuaste en consecuencia."

# game/episode018.rpy:1204
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_9fef6ff7:

#   ra "I guess so."
    ra "Supongo que sí."

# game/episode018.rpy:1205
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_65c4acaf:

#   c "That first step must have been so hard for you."
    c "Ese primer paso debió de ser muy duro para ti."

# game/episode018.rpy:1206
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_ad0bba1e:

#   c "Deeply enmeshed in your father's religious bullshit regarding the person you really are."
    c "Profundamente enredado en la mierda religiosa de tu padre respecto a la persona que realmente eres."

# game/episode018.rpy:1207
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_72a0dfb0:

#   c "And yet you reached out, asked for help."
    c "Y, sin embargo, te acercaste, pediste ayuda."

# game/episode018.rpy:1208
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_f470a68a:

#   c "I think that speaks volumes of you, Raene."
    c "Creo que eso dice mucho de ti, Raene."

# game/episode018.rpy:1209
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_0c2753c7:

#   ra "It does?"
    ra "¿Sí?"

# game/episode018.rpy:1210
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_9ed06a5b:

#   c "Yes, that you're a strong woman, not deterred by the opinions of others."
    c "Sí, que eres una mujer fuerte, que no se deja amilanar por las opiniones de los demás."

# game/episode018.rpy:1211
translate spanish ep018_ruins_raene_7fd1be88:

